You'll be dead if you go there

271
00:22:22.260 --> 00:22:24.260
We can't just sit here and watch TV!

272
00:22:24.295 --> 00:22:27.763
This Kira might be able to kill just by seeing the faces

273
00:22:28.230 --> 00:22:32.442
The the policemen near the scene to keep away

274
00:22:33.240 --> 00:22:35.200
Yes

275
00:22:36.240 --> 00:22:38.210
Ryuzaki...!

276
00:22:40.240 --> 00:22:44.200
We must fight with Kira

277
00:22:45.250 --> 00:22:47.250
But

278
00:22:47.285 --> 00:22:49.250
We must rescue Sayu!

279
00:22:49.285 --> 00:22:51.260
This Kira's targets

280
00:22:51.295 --> 00:22:53.260
are people who interrupt the broadcasting

281
00:22:53.295 --> 00:22:56.260
Sayu should be safe

282
00:22:56.295 --> 00:22:58.260
And Kira. if you're watching TV.

283
00:22:58.295 --> 00:23:00.270
Come here now

284
00:23:00.305 --> 00:23:03.916
I promise I will help you

285
00:23:05.127 --> 00:23:08.685
As you see. I have the eye

286
00:23:09.240 --> 00:23:13.200
Let me see your Reaper. then I'll show you mine

287
00:23:15.250 --> 00:23:17.220
Reaper��

288
00:23:18.250 --> 00:23:20.671
Do you expect me to believe that such things really exist?

289
00:23:21.260 --> 00:23:23.981
It must mean the ability of killing

290
00:23:26.260 --> 00:23:30.021
And let's create a new world together!

291
00:23:32.270 --> 00:23:34.240
What do you mean by the new world!

292
00:23:34.275 --> 00:23:36.240
You murderer!

293
00:23:36.275 --> 00:23:39.240
How can you kill people so easily?

294
00:23:39.872 --> 00:23:42.121
What did they do to you��

295
00:23:42.250 --> 00:23:44.210
Murderer!

296
00:23:45.250 --> 00:23:47.250
Murderer!

297
00:23:47.285 --> 00:23:49.249
Sayu...! Don't upset him!

298
00:23:54.260 --> 00:23:56.230
Murderer

299
00:23:58.260 --> 00:24:00.230
Murderer��

300
00:24:01.270 --> 00:24:03.230
Murderer

301
00:24:18.250 --> 00:24:20.220
Murderer!

302
00:24:55.971 --> 00:24:57.597
What are you doing!

303
00:25:13.280 --> 00:25:17.220
A car just crashed into the station

304
00:25:18.250 --> 00:25:20.250
We don't know yet what exactly happened

305
00:25:20.285 --> 00:25:22.220
Is that..

306
00:25:23.260 --> 00:25:24.266
really?

307
00:25:27.896 --> 00:25:28.725
Sayu!

308
00:25:29.260 --> 00:25:30.416
Dad?

309
00:25:34.270 --> 00:25:34.892
Cover your face with this

310
00:25:36.270 --> 00:25:38.240
go inside

311
00:25:45.280 --> 00:25:47.220
Mogi..

312
00:26:04.270 --> 00:26:09.469
We'll inform you as soon as we find out what is happening at the entrance

313
00:26:13.280 --> 00:26:16.280
Alright. cut to commercials

314
00:26:16.315 --> 00:26:19.290
The ratings will be 30... no. 40 at least

315
00:26:19.325 --> 00:26:21.220
L's message earned 35%

316
00:26:23.260 --> 00:26:25.260
You can't go in

317
00:26:25.295 --> 00:26:27.230
Step aside

318
00:26:28.260 --> 00:26:30.270
Is that you?

319
00:26:30.305 --> 00:26:32.270
You're the producer��

320
00:26:32.305 --> 00:26:33.538
You can't enter without...

321
00:26:34.270 --> 00:26:37.187
The police��Stop broadcasting now!

322
00:26:38.270 --> 00:26:39.490
If we do that. we're gonna die

323
00:26:40.185 --> 00:26:41.608
You want to see innocent people...

324
00:26:42.223 --> 00:26:43.274
forced to get involved and killed?

325
00:26:44.280 --> 00:26:45.198
I got it!

326
00:26:45.881 --> 00:26:46.779
Calm down��

327
00:26:49.290 --> 00:26:50.562
Got it..

328
00:26:52.290 --> 00:26:53.294
Hello?

329
00:26:53.992 --> 00:26:54.662
Thank you

330
00:26:58.779 --> 00:27:01.355
Ryuzaki. I told them to stop broadcasting

331
00:27:01.390 --> 00:27:03.749
I go the videotapes too

332
00:27:04.056 --> 00:27:04.918
This is as I thought

333
00:27:05.162 --> 00:27:05.978
It was Mr. yagami!

334
00:27:06.751 --> 00:27:08.846
I can't do this in such as way

335
00:27:09.067 --> 00:27:10.738
Dad. where is Sayu? Is she alright?

336
00:27:11.280 --> 00:27:12.415
Light..

337
00:27:13.842 --> 00:27:15.927
Yes. we're both fine

338
00:27:16.280 --> 00:27:19.458
Mr. Yagami. are you still wearing a helmet?

339
00:27:20.286 --> 00:27:22.076
No. I took it off

340
00:27:22.290 --> 00:27:23.702
I'll go pick them up

341
00:27:24.290 --> 00:27:25.724
Please arrange for the permission to enter the studio

342
00:27:25.725 --> 00:27:26.894
You'll be Kira's target!

343
00:27:27.092 --> 00:27:29.101
Dad and Sayu will not be harmed inside the studio

344
00:27:37.270 --> 00:27:40.155
The Second Kira surely has the Reaper's eye

345
00:27:40.280 --> 00:27:43.073
You've got a nice buddy huh?

346
00:27:43.108 --> 00:27:44.280
No

347
00:27:44.315 --> 00:27:46.790
There's no proof that he's not my enemy

348
00:27:47.290 --> 00:27:49.231
Then isn't it dangerous to go?

349
00:27:49.290 --> 00:27:52.956
If he truely supports me. he'll be a strong weapon to wipe out L

350
00:27:53.290 --> 00:27:55.201
I must find him before L does

351
00:27:58.300 --> 00:28:00.270
Move out

352
00:28:07.270 --> 00:28:11.230
Sakura TV has stopped broadcasting. following the order from the police

353
00:28:12.280 --> 00:28:14.280
Taiyo TV

354
00:28:14.315 --> 00:28:16.280
is protesting against Sakura TV

355
00:28:16.315 --> 00:28:18.290
According to Taiyo TV

356
00:28:18.325 --> 00:28:22.250
Mr. Hibima died because of Sakura TV

357
00:28:26.300 --> 00:28:28.884
Misa. the recording is cancelled

358
00:28:29.300 --> 00:28:31.300
yeah. alright

359
00:28:31.335 --> 00:28:32.860
It can't be helped

360
00:28:34.145 --> 00:28:35.022
I need to change clothes

361
00:28:44.877 --> 00:28:47.578
The Kira didn't show up

362
00:29:08.280 --> 00:29:10.240
-Sayu
-Light

363
00:29:11.280 --> 00:29:12.928
I was worried about you

364
00:29:12.963 --> 00:29:13.789
Mr. Mogi..

365
00:29:14.212 --> 00:29:15.250
He was killed��

366
00:29:23.290 --> 00:29:26.300
Yes. I will report it

367
00:29:26.335 --> 00:29:28.260
Excuse me

368
00:29:44.280 --> 00:29:46.250
Kira...?

369
00:29:48.290 --> 00:29:49.922
I found you

370
00:29:51.070 --> 00:29:52.933
I knew he'd come to me

371
00:29:57.300 --> 00:29:59.095
Yagami...

372
00:30:01.300 --> 00:30:02.395
Tsuki?

373
00:30:08.310 --> 00:30:10.310
The videotapes were dispatched

374
00:30:10.663 --> 00:30:13.663
at a post office in Kita-ku Osaka

375
00:30:13.310 --> 00:30:15.280
The fingerprints are so small

376
00:30:15.315 --> 00:30:18.290
so 'he' might be 'she'

377
00:30:18.325 --> 00:30:22.290
Are you sure that these are from the Second Kira?

378
00:30:22.325 --> 00:30:25.290
It may be a fake

379
00:30:25.325 --> 00:30:29.300
You mean. this might be a fake by Kira that there are more Kiras?

380
00:30:29.335 --> 00:30:31.385
Light. what do you think?

381
00:30:33.300 --> 00:30:33.992
That's impossible

382
00:30:34.365 --> 00:30:36.654
And this Kira can kill only by seeing the faces

383
00:30:37.310 --> 00:30:39.310
The video images were childish.

384
00:30:39.345 --> 00:30:41.310
trying to use the media slyly

385
00:30:41.345 --> 00:30:44.310
This Kira is way stupid and different from the first Kira

386
00:30:44.709 --> 00:30:48.427
Besides. the first Kira doesn't kill innocent people

387
00:30:49.290 --> 00:30:50.274
You're right

388
00:30:50.309 --> 00:30:53.512
If I were Kira. I'd get angry

389
00:30:55.290 --> 00:30:57.300
This Kira tried to make us believe that he was outside the studio

390
00:30:57.335 --> 00:30:59.300
Had the studio on surveillance

391
00:30:59.335 --> 00:31:02.300
He could be hidden inside the studio

392
00:31:02.335 --> 00:31:04.323
Check everyone in the studio

393
00:31:06.310 --> 00:31:09.236
If the first Kira joins the second Kira

394
00:31:09.237 --> 00:31:11.644
It will be a huge threat

395
00:31:12.914 --> 00:31:14.813
We must prevent it. Mr Yagami..

396
00:31:14.848 --> 00:31:17.746
Is it possible to send Kira a message through TV?

397
00:31:18.320 --> 00:31:20.714
What kind of message?

398
00:31:25.528 --> 00:31:28.314
Nishiyama Saeko is the No. 1 anchorwoman in Japan

399
00:31:29.300 --> 00:31:30.099
Thank you so much

400
00:31:30.906 --> 00:31:33.746
That's clever... You're the man. Demegawa

401
00:31:35.541 --> 00:31:37.501
How can they be so blind?

402
00:31:38.871 --> 00:31:41.952
The Second Kira trusted and sent the tapes to us

403
00:31:42.310 --> 00:31:45.786
because you've been reporting on the First Kira's activities

404
00:31:46.320 --> 00:31:49.886
They should appreciate you

405
00:31:50.320 --> 00:31:51.993
Irritating��

406
00:31:53.330 --> 00:31:56.017
Why didn't you become an anchor?

407
00:31:56.300 --> 00:31:58.438
See how Saeko behaves?

408
00:31:59.399 --> 00:32:01.399
To be an anchor. you have to sell youself as a 'female'

409
00:32:01.300 --> 00:32:03.200
I can't stand it

410
00:32:04.300 --> 00:32:06.740
You're prettier than her

411
00:32:07.310 --> 00:32:08.582
Give me a break

412
00:32:10.310 --> 00:32:10.878
Demegawa!

413
00:32:11.445 --> 00:32:12.985
Did you survive the torture by the police?

414
00:32:13.642 --> 00:32:15.783
Yeah. and more than that

415
00:32:16.320 --> 00:32:18.121
I got a sweet gift from them

416
00:32:18.320 --> 00:32:18.980
What's that?

417
00:32:18.983 --> 00:32:21.351
That's a message from the police to the Second Kira

418
00:32:21.937 --> 00:32:23.095
We can expect high ratings

419
00:32:23.330 --> 00:32:25.290
Great job!

420
00:32:26.330 --> 00:32:28.755
This is a message for the Second Kira

421
00:32:29.300 --> 00:32:31.300
Stop trying to approach the First Kira

422
00:32:31.335 --> 00:32:33.270
It's not too late if you haven't met him

423
00:32:34.300 --> 00:32:38.310
You must never get involved in Kira just because you're curious

424
00:32:38.345 --> 00:32:40.310
You'll be used

425
00:32:40.345 --> 00:32:42.310
and definitely killed by Kira

426
00:32:42.345 --> 00:32:44.280
Yagami Light....

427
00:32:48.320 --> 00:32:51.736
It's written "Moon"
but read "Light"

428
00:32:52.320 --> 00:32:55.330
"...please provide us with any information regarding Kira"

429
00:32:55.365 --> 00:32:57.330
"... save those living under Kira's terrorist acts"

430
00:32:57.365 --> 00:32:59.362
"... and save the world"

431
00:33:00.209 --> 00:33:02.276
Reating the message...

432
00:33:06.310 --> 00:33:08.310
Here is the data for every staff at Sakura TV

433
00:33:08.345 --> 00:33:11.067
and the list of people who entered the studio that day

434
00:33:11.293 --> 00:33:12.611
What a huge amount

435
00:33:14.046 --> 00:33:15.182
That total...

436
00:33:15.811 --> 00:33:17.784
8000 people. approximately.

437
00:33:18.320 --> 00:33:18.970
Let's start

438
00:33:36.310 --> 00:33:38.280
Oh. good evening!

439
00:33:39.310 --> 00:33:42.247
Nice to meet you. I'm Amane Misa

440
00:33:44.320 --> 00:33:45.735
You're a friend of Sayu?

441
00:33:46.320 --> 00:33:47.387
Oh. no

442
00:33:48.320 --> 00:33:51.266
I was watching TV and... I thought you must be worried.

443
00:33:52.085 --> 00:33:54.251
I couldn't help come to see you

444
00:33:56.330 --> 00:33:58.310
to show you this notebook

445
00:34:01.340 --> 00:34:02.794
Here. touch it

446
00:34:14.320 --> 00:34:16.617
Light. you're back!

447
00:34:17.320 --> 00:34:19.320
She's my friend.

448
00:34:19.355 --> 00:34:21.373
She'll come to my room for a while

449
00:34:23.330 --> 00:34:25.376
Hello

450
00:34:26.330 --> 00:34:27.899
Light. did you invite a friend?

451
00:34:29.162 --> 00:34:30.486
Nice to meet you

452
00:34:40.340 --> 00:34:42.502
Her face looks familiar...

453
00:34:42.537 --> 00:34:45.806
She's Misa-misa! of the Happy Sweets!

454
00:34:46.320 --> 00:34:48.705
Yeah! Amane Misa!

455
00:35:01.921 --> 00:35:03.082
How did you know it?

456
00:35:04.071 --> 00:35:05.207
Ah. that's what I thought!

457
00:35:05.242 --> 00:35:07.652
You haven't done 'the deal'

458
00:35:08.231 --> 00:35:11.431
You know. you can see people's names and their lifespan

459
00:35:12.201 --> 00:35:15.029
but you can't see the lifespan of a person who has the notebook

460
00:35:16.320 --> 00:35:19.982
I couldn't answer unless you ask me

461
00:35:22.330 --> 00:35:26.473
Are you... working in the studio or something?

462
00:35:27.330 --> 00:35:31.290
um... I... I think I'm kind of famous..

463
00:35:36.340 --> 00:35:37.027
A singer?

464
00:35:37.062 --> 00:35:39.037
Oh. actually. this is my first CD.

465
00:35:40.350 --> 00:35:42.350
I also appear on magazine and TV.

466
00:35:42.385 --> 00:35:44.047
Oh. there's a new movie too

467
00:35:44.350 --> 00:35:47.016
How did you find out where I live?

468
00:35:48.320 --> 00:35:50.320
From the internet.

469
00:35:50.355 --> 00:35:52.320
You gave a speech at the entrance ceremony of college

470
00:35:52.330 --> 00:35:54.330
I found a photo of you there

471
00:35:54.365 --> 00:35:57.330
If you were arrested.

472
00:35:57.365 --> 00:35:58.719
Kira's secrets would come out!

473
00:35:59.330 --> 00:36:01.330
I'm sorry!

474
00:36:01.340 --> 00:36:04.340
But I haven't been arrested

475
00:36:04.375 --> 00:36:07.067
and I won't be if I follow your orders from now on

476
00:36:07.850 --> 00:36:08.720
Right?

477
00:36:13.350 --> 00:36:15.186
I can find out L's name

478
00:36:16.350 --> 00:36:18.350
I'll be your eyes. So...

479
00:36:20.360 --> 00:36:22.290
So what?

480
00:36:24.330 --> 00:36:26.343
Let me be your girlfriend

481
00:36:29.330 --> 00:36:30.524
I can't

482
00:36:30.811 --> 00:36:31.972
Why not?

483
00:36:32.276 --> 00:36:34.544
There are your fingerprints on the tapes

484
00:36:35.013 --> 00:36:37.774
If the police take fingerprints directly from you.

485
00:36:37.340 --> 00:36:39.766
they'll find out you're the Second Kira.

486
00:36:40.350 --> 00:36:42.255
Those weren't mine!

487
00:36:43.101 --> 00:36:45.076
I'm not that stupid

488
00:36:45.350 --> 00:36:48.350
I have a friend in Osaka who's into the occult

489
00:36:48.385 --> 00:36:50.360
and I showed her fake pictures of ghosts

490
00:36:50.395 --> 00:36:53.360
and asked her to send videos to TV stations together...

491
00:36:53.395 --> 00:36:55.977
And what is she doing now?

492
00:36:56.330 --> 00:37:00.276
If you want. I'll kill her right now

493
00:37:01.166 --> 00:37:04.176
No. The police'll easily link her to you

494
00:37:06.340 --> 00:37:08.867
If you don't believe me...

495
00:37:09.340 --> 00:37:12.838
You can keep my Death Note

496
00:37:14.350 --> 00:37:16.350
I'm still the owner of the notebook even if you keep it.

497
00:37:16.385 --> 00:37:19.350
So I can still work my eyes for you.

498
00:37:19.838 --> 00:37:21.234
Right Remu?

499
00:37:21.673 --> 00:37:23.356
Yes. you're right

500
00:37:26.760 --> 00:37:29.842
Now. I can't kill you

501
00:37:30.208 --> 00:37:32.628
and you can kill me if you don't need me

502
00:37:39.740 --> 00:37:41.329
I'm happy...

503
00:37:42.290 --> 00:37:44.932
...even if you're just going to use me

504
00:37:47.174 --> 00:37:48.590
Trust me

505
00:37:52.760 --> 00:37:54.105
Why are you doing this?

506
00:37:57.760 --> 00:38:00.397
Misa lost all of her family members 3 years ago

507
00:38:00.432 --> 00:38:02.480
They were killed by a burglar

508
00:38:15.750 --> 00:38:18.750
Since Misa had seen his face

509
00:38:18.760 --> 00:38:20.655
The suspect was soon arrested

510
00:38:21.760 --> 00:38:24.760
But Misa was the only witness so it wasn't enough to convict him

511
00:38:25.834 --> 00:38:29.482
Tamura Yoichi. the suspect was soon released

512
00:38:35.740 --> 00:38:39.700
She was caught in a deep empty darkness in her mind

513
00:38:40.750 --> 00:38:43.788
Everyone gave up on Misa's future

514
00:38:44.338 --> 00:38:46.265
But one day.

515
00:38:45.750 --> 00:38:49.459
Something happened

516
00:38:54.524 --> 00:38:56.706
"Tamura Yoichi Found Dead"

517
00:38:58.140 --> 00:39:00.018
"Is This Kira?"

518
00:39:02.770 --> 00:39:05.809
Kira punished him

519
00:39:06.842 --> 00:39:10.393
Misa was grateful to the God named Kira

520
00:39:20.238 --> 00:39:21.107
Please

521
00:39:24.242 --> 00:39:26.414
Trust me

522
00:39:29.770 --> 00:39:31.764
You are everything to me

523
00:39:31.770 --> 00:39:34.567
But you killed innocent policemen

524
00:39:35.592 --> 00:39:39.105
Don't you think it's the same as the burglar who killed your family?

525
00:39:39.808 --> 00:39:42.105
Don't say such things to me?

526
00:39:44.750 --> 00:39:46.750
You also think that..

527
00:39:46.785 --> 00:39:50.202
...sacrifices for the good of all can't be helped

528
00:39:53.760 --> 00:39:57.720
It was the only thing I could do

529
00:39:58.770 --> 00:40:01.369
I really wanted to see you

530
00:40:10.303 --> 00:40:11.645
I understand

531
00:40:14.354 --> 00:40:16.045
For me...

532
00:40:16.779 --> 00:40:18.810
You shortened your own life...

533
00:40:20.120 --> 00:40:22.208
Your eyes became my weapon

534
00:40:22.450 --> 00:40:24.215
Thank you...

535
00:40:29.491 --> 00:40:31.153
I'll do my best

536
00:40:33.205 --> 00:40:35.175
to be loved by you..

537
00:40:48.925 --> 00:40:50.706
I'll arrange a chance for you to see L.

538
00:40:50.895 --> 00:40:53.895
And you'll see L's real name

539
00:40:53.930 --> 00:40:55.808
Can you do it?

540
00:40:56.797 --> 00:40:59.674
You don't have to ask me. just say "do it"

541
00:40:59.968 --> 00:41:03.390
I'll do anything you want me to

542
00:41:03.757 --> 00:41:06.237
If one of us gets arrested

543
00:41:05.905 --> 00:41:08.915
we'll never talk about the other one and the Death Note

544
00:41:08.950 --> 00:41:11.122
Can you swear?

545
00:41:11.915 --> 00:41:13.654
Yes. I swear

546
00:41:13.915 --> 00:41:15.354
Good

547
00:41:18.925 --> 00:41:21.071
Then... It's my turn

548
00:41:22.925 --> 00:41:26.339
We're gonna date at least once a week

549
00:41:27.680 --> 00:41:29.888
You don't understand what I said

550
00:41:29.905 --> 00:41:31.905
But once L dies.

551
00:41:31.940 --> 00:41:33.671
There won't be no difficulty between us. right?

552
00:41:33.905 --> 00:41:36.315
You underestimate L

553
00:41:36.808 --> 00:41:38.324
Besides L is already...

554
00:41:38.915 --> 00:41:41.296
Suspecting that I am Kira

555
00:41:41.297 --> 00:41:42.297
What?

556
00:41:43.978 --> 00:41:45.604
L is so smart

557
00:41:46.626 --> 00:41:50.470
Everybody says L hasn't figured out anything yet...

558
00:41:50.505 --> 00:41:53.864
Now I've reached a position where I can contact him directly.

559
00:41:53.925 --> 00:41:56.505
L and Kira are getting closer...?

560
00:41:59.578 --> 00:42:01.191
I'm impressed by both!

561
00:42:01.192 --> 00:42:02.587
It's so exciting

562
00:42:02.905 --> 00:42:05.063
And of course. I need you to kill L.

563
00:42:05.558 --> 00:42:07.533
So I wanted to contact you as quickly as possible

564
00:42:07.568 --> 00:42:10.301
If so. why just can't we date?

565
00:42:10.336 --> 00:42:11.915
If you want to date once a week

566
00:42:11.950 --> 00:42:15.915
I'll have to date other girls

567
00:42:15.950 --> 00:42:17.925
to avoid being suspected that we have a special relationship

568
00:42:17.960 --> 00:42:19.885
You can't do that

569
00:42:20.925 --> 00:42:22.925
If I see you dating other girl..

570
00:42:22.960 --> 00:42:25.424
I'll kill her!

571
00:42:25.935 --> 00:42:28.358
I'm the only one who'll date you!

572
00:42:28.935 --> 00:42:31.449
If you don't obey me. I have to kill you

573
00:42:33.905 --> 00:42:35.905
I won't let you kill her. Yagami Light!

574
00:42:37.915 --> 00:42:39.915
If you harm this girl.

575
00:42:39.950 --> 00:42:41.737
I won't forgive you

576
00:42:42.307 --> 00:42:44.553
I see her lifespan

577
00:42:45.423 --> 00:42:48.850
If she dies. I'll think it's because you killed her. I'll have to kill you

578
00:42:48.925 --> 00:42:51.870
If I find you trying to kill her..

579
00:42:51.925 --> 00:42:54.950
I'll kill you before that happens

580
00:43:12.915 --> 00:43:14.273
Ryuzaki...?

581
00:43:15.915 --> 00:43:19.534
Since that. there's no new action by the Second Kira

582
00:43:19.989 --> 00:43:24.771
I'm afriad the FIrst and the Second Kira have made contact already

583
00:43:25.760 --> 00:43:28.099
Isn't it careless to expose your face?

584
00:43:28.134 --> 00:43:31.022
Yes. it's dangerous if you're Kira

585
00:43:31.565 --> 00:43:35.596
You're the only one outside who knows that I'm L. so

586
00:43:36.688 --> 00:43:40.341
If you told the Second Kira about me. it's "the end." To avoid it.

587
00:43:40.915 --> 00:43:42.885
I brought this

588
00:43:45.556 --> 00:43:46.722
That'll work

589
00:43:48.925 --> 00:43:50.405
Did you come to watch over me?

590
00:43:50.925 --> 00:43:53.526
You think Kira is a college student. don't you?

591
00:43:53.925 --> 00:43:56.935
I have an important job here

592
00:43:56.970 --> 00:43:58.227
About Kira?

593
00:44:00.382 --> 00:44:02.352
Light

594
00:44:04.945 --> 00:44:07.168
I had a recording nearby so I came to see you

595
00:44:07.203 --> 00:44:08.015
Here I am

596
00:44:09.915 --> 00:44:10.814
You

597
00:44:17.098 --> 00:44:18.140
Oh?

598
00:44:18.925 --> 00:44:21.078
Are you Light's friend?

599
00:44:21.782 --> 00:44:22.467
Yeah

600
00:44:24.935 --> 00:44:26.879
His name is Ryuzaki

601
00:44:28.935 --> 00:44:31.680
Why're you wearing such as stupid mask?

602
00:44:31.935 --> 00:44:34.328
Why don't you take it off?

603
00:44:36.945 --> 00:44:37.888
Hi there!

604
00:44:39.945 --> 00:44:41.693
Are you... Ryuzaki...?

605
00:44:49.994 --> 00:44:52.414
Nice to meet you.
I'm Amane Misa

606
00:44:53.925 --> 00:44:57.220
Um... Light?
Your friend is a little weird

607
00:44:57.935 --> 00:44:59.415
He's just shy

608
00:45:03.945 --> 00:45:05.668
I envy you Light

609
00:45:09.945 --> 00:45:11.631
I listen to your Heaven's Door!

610
00:45:11.945 --> 00:45:14.697
Really?
I'm so glad!

611
00:45:15.582 --> 00:45:19.512
Light. why can you date with such a cute pop star?

612
00:45:19.925 --> 00:45:22.033
I approached him first

613
00:45:22.068 --> 00:45:23.498
Misa!

614
00:45:23.499 --> 00:45:25.271
Look. isn't that Misa-Misa?

615
00:45:26.935 --> 00:45:28.402
She really is!

616
00:45:29.935 --> 00:45:31.905
Why! Why is she here?

617
00:45:33.945 --> 00:45:35.945
This is great

618
00:45:35.980 --> 00:45:37.915
It's real

619
00:45:42.618 --> 00:45:46.649
You're the most intelligent students in Japan. right?

620
00:45:46.684 --> 00:45:48.103
Please shake hands with me

621
00:45:50.316 --> 00:45:53.040
Oh! Someone touched my bottom!

622
00:45:53.935 --> 00:45:55.393
Can't forgive him!

623
00:45:56.383 --> 00:45:59.251
I. the greatest detective. will definitely catch the pervert!

624
00:45:59.935 --> 00:46:00.736
Here you go

625
00:46:02.670 --> 00:46:04.123
Ryuzaki. you're funny

626
00:46:04.133 --> 00:46:07.133
Then. don't you want to date with me?

627
00:46:07.945 --> 00:46:10.637
Too bad. here's my only sweet heart

628
00:46:11.246 --> 00:46:12.582
Whaaat?

629
00:46:13.097 --> 00:46:15.347
I have a class. so go back to your work

630
00:46:15.768 --> 00:46:16.593
Right

631
00:46:16.955 --> 00:46:19.527
Sorry. but I'm glad to see you

632
00:46:19.955 --> 00:46:21.363
See you soon. Light

633
00:46:29.935 --> 00:46:31.935
It's good...

634
00:46:31.970 --> 00:46:33.905
She's so cute

635
00:46:37.945 --> 00:46:39.234
Ryuzaki

636
00:46:39.945 --> 00:46:41.596
She's my girlfriend

637
00:46:42.669 --> 00:46:43.549
bye

638
00:46:44.394 --> 00:46:45.909
It was lucky to see Misa-Misa.

639
00:46:44.955 --> 00:46:46.925
I'll go back to the office

640
00:46:48.955 --> 00:46:49.788
Take care

641
00:46:56.935 --> 00:46:57.894
I won...!

642
00:47:02.076 --> 00:47:04.448
"Misa"

643
00:47:18.955 --> 00:47:20.041
Hello

644
00:47:24.965 --> 00:47:27.375
What are you doing?

645
00:47:30.935 --> 00:47:34.895
Someone dropped this cell phone and I picked it up

646
00:47:35.945 --> 00:47:37.526
It belongs to Misa

647
00:47:38.644 --> 00:47:39.966
Give it to me

648
00:47:51.965 --> 00:47:54.850
Calling her just after you said goodbye?

649
00:47:55.384 --> 00:47:57.449
You really are in love with her
Or.

650
00:47:58.031 --> 00:48:01.029
Was there anything you had to ask her immediately

651
00:48:09.650 --> 00:48:10.798
Hello

652
00:48:11.051 --> 00:48:12.667
We have the target.

653
00:48:13.707 --> 00:48:15.707
It wasn't the place we expected

654
00:48:15.955 --> 00:48:17.371
since she moved around so much

655
00:48:17.955 --> 00:48:20.394
We'll send her to the office

656
00:48:20.597 --> 00:48:23.589
I got it
Thank you for the hard work

657
00:48:25.965 --> 00:48:27.076
Just now

658
00:48:27.077 --> 00:48:31.086
We arrested Amane Misa for the suspicion to be the Second Kira

659
00:48:31.975 --> 00:48:32.938
What?

660
00:48:35.864 --> 00:48:40.395
She is an enthusiastic supporter of Kira and she was in the studio that day

661
00:48:41.363 --> 00:48:42.888
From her room.

662
00:48:41.955 --> 00:48:44.955
We found material evidences such as a cosmetic powder

663
00:48:44.990 --> 00:48:47.955
and fibers matching her clothes

664
00:48:48.481 --> 00:48:51.838
We're not going to announce so please cooperate for awhile

665
00:48:53.068 --> 00:48:56.110
You have to stay away from the office

666
00:48:56.965 --> 00:48:58.348
What are you going to do to her?

667
00:48:58.752 --> 00:49:02.748
I can't tell you.
Can I take her phone too?

668
00:49:05.487 --> 00:49:07.251
I can't believe she's the Kira

669
00:49:08.985 --> 00:49:09.179
It can't be

670
00:49:14.261 --> 00:49:15.901
Awwww. Light

671
00:49:16.190 --> 00:49:19.828
The goddess of the luck is gone

672
00:49:21.398 --> 00:49:22.527
See you

673
00:50:09.985 --> 00:50:10.665
Ryuzaki

674
00:50:12.085 --> 00:50:14.732
Do we really have to do this?

675
00:50:15.498 --> 00:50:17.931
Second Kira can kill by seeing the face

676
00:50:17.966 --> 00:50:21.880
It's reasonable to restrain her with a 24 hour surveillance

677
00:50:23.076 --> 00:50:26.076
If she isn't Kira...

678
00:50:24.965 --> 00:50:27.618
This will violate human rights

679
00:50:28.139 --> 00:50:29.502
We've got the evidence!

680
00:50:29.975 --> 00:50:32.975
Besides she stays silent even in this situation

681
00:50:33.010 --> 00:50:35.975
If she's innocent. why doesn't she just say so

682
00:50:37.544 --> 00:50:39.544
Tell her agent to announce

683
00:50:37.985 --> 00:50:41.467
that she's in hospital

684
00:50:42.157 --> 00:50:43.579
It's already done

685
00:50:45.142 --> 00:50:46.124
Mr. Yagami

686
00:50:46.810 --> 00:50:50.364
Amane and Light have a close relationship

687
00:50:52.023 --> 00:50:52.725
What?

688
00:50:54.010 --> 00:50:57.365
She's even visited your home. Mr. Yagami

689
00:50:58.023 --> 00:50:59.626
Light...

690
00:51:04.033 --> 00:51:06.033
I have to contact Rem

691
00:51:08.529 --> 00:51:08.529
before Misa talks them about the secrets...

692
00:51:09.033 --> 00:51:10.986
It's gonna get worse

693
00:51:11.473 --> 00:51:15.433
We can't part from the owner of the Death Note

694
00:51:18.043 --> 00:51:21.306
Unless the owner abandons the right of possession or...

695
00:51:21.955 --> 00:51:23.601
dies

696
00:51:40.043 --> 00:51:43.689
She hasn't eaten anything in 2 days

697
00:51:44.868 --> 00:51:47.394
She has a lot of guts..
She doesn't even complain

698
00:51:49.241 --> 00:51:51.041
I'm... becoming a fan of her

699
00:51:53.053 --> 00:51:53.689
I'm going to buy her CD

700
00:51:54.204 --> 00:51:55.024
Idiot!

701
00:51:56.682 --> 00:51:58.178
Toilet...

702
00:51:59.446 --> 00:52:01.303
I want to use the toilet

703
00:52:08.302 --> 00:52:09.222
Even after she got caught.

704
00:52:09.223 --> 00:52:11.604
Kira hasn't stopped punishing

705
00:52:16.716 --> 00:52:17.458
Here

706
00:52:20.726 --> 00:52:22.050
Misa

707
00:52:25.226 --> 00:52:27.236
Please...

708
00:52:27.271 --> 00:52:29.196
Say something...

709
00:52:31.206 --> 00:52:32.866
We don't want to..

710
00:52:32.867 --> 00:52:35.553
make you suffer anymore

711
00:52:39.216 --> 00:52:40.399
What do you...

712
00:52:41.213 --> 00:52:43.062
know about Kira?

713
00:52:46.216 --> 00:52:47.806
I can't stand this anymore

714
00:52:48.226 --> 00:52:49.747
kill me

715
00:52:51.226 --> 00:52:53.054
kill me

716
00:52:55.226 --> 00:52:57.167
We must release her!

717
00:52:58.236 --> 00:53:00.461
Amane Misa. do you hear me?

718
00:53:01.236 --> 00:53:03.206
Please

719
00:53:04.206 --> 00:53:06.176
kill me

720
00:53:10.216 --> 00:53:13.589
Do you mean that you admit you're the Second Kira?

721
00:53:14.099 --> 00:53:16.301
It doesn't matter if I'm Kira or not

722
00:53:18.226 --> 00:53:20.688
If I have to live like this...

723
00:53:23.725 --> 00:53:25.275
I'd rather die

724
00:53:29.605 --> 00:53:30.171
Hey!

725
00:53:32.591 --> 00:53:34.339
kill me now

726
00:53:37.139 --> 00:53:39.929
You're able to kill me easily!

727
00:53:43.277 --> 00:53:47.134
I should have died that time anyway

728
00:53:50.226 --> 00:53:52.519
I'm happy even if I die now

729
00:53:55.821 --> 00:53:58.608
kill me before I get old and lose my beauty

730
00:54:01.236 --> 00:54:03.206
kill me right now

731
00:54:18.226 --> 00:54:20.226
Rem..

732
00:54:20.261 --> 00:54:23.794
Misa abandoned the possessive right of the Death Note

733
00:54:25.736 --> 00:54:28.784
She asked me to kill her

734
00:54:29.454 --> 00:54:31.522
because she didn't want you to get in trouble

735
00:54:31.557 --> 00:54:34.227
Do you understand. Yagami Light?

736
00:54:35.207 --> 00:54:37.788
Everything she did was to be loved by you

737
00:54:39.216 --> 00:54:40.154
Did she...

738
00:54:41.733 --> 00:54:44.940
lose all the memory about the Death Note?

739
00:54:45.131 --> 00:54:46.207
Of course

740
00:54:46.565 --> 00:54:48.549
She forgot that she has killed people

741
00:54:48.226 --> 00:54:51.591
or that you are Kira

742
00:54:52.923 --> 00:54:55.300
I told her that she'd never see me anymore

743
00:54:55.335 --> 00:55:00.468
and all she'd remember is that she loves Yagami Light

744
00:55:01.286 --> 00:55:04.363
Misa answered it would be fine

745
00:55:09.246 --> 00:55:11.908
Save her at all cost!

746
00:55:12.246 --> 00:55:15.169
If you don't. I'll kill you

747
00:55:16.256 --> 00:55:18.840
With a Death God being so nice to her..

748
00:55:19.919 --> 00:55:21.461
Misa must be very happy

749
00:55:21.496 --> 00:55:25.669
I am just trying to keep the promise with Jealous

750
00:55:28.236 --> 00:55:29.705
Jealous��

751
00:55:30.236 --> 00:55:34.033
Jealous was always looking down on Misa

752
00:55:34.236 --> 00:55:39.177
He had a father-like sympathy towards the girl who lost her parents

753
00:55:39.944 --> 00:55:43.926
However. when the time comes when Misa would die

754
00:55:45.364 --> 00:55:49.687
Eventually. he broke the rules of the Death Gods

755
00:55:50.226 --> 00:55:53.226
He wrote the name of the man

756
00:55:53.261 --> 00:55:56.840
and extended Misa's lifespan

757
00:55:57.236 --> 00:56:02.690
The Death Gods exist only to take lives of humans

758
00:56:03.236 --> 00:56:05.246
It's a serious taboo to save a human

759
00:56:05.281 --> 00:56:08.424
and extend her lifespan

760
00:56:09.246 --> 00:56:11.850
Jealous fell to pieces and died

761
00:56:12.997 --> 00:56:16.108
asking me to take care of her

762
00:56:16.570 --> 00:56:17.670
Therefore

763
00:56:18.259 --> 00:56:20.628
Jealous's Death Note was given to Misa

764
00:56:22.266 --> 00:56:26.196
A Death God who falls in love with a human shall die...

765
00:56:30.236 --> 00:56:32.236
a great story. indeed

766
00:56:33.259 --> 00:56:35.269
If you won't save Misa.

767
00:56:34.246 --> 00:56:36.206
I will kill you

768
00:56:37.246 --> 00:56:40.234
Don't give me the same phrase over and over again. Rem

769
00:56:41.007 --> 00:56:43.267
Imagine how she feels if I die

770
00:56:44.754 --> 00:56:46.617
She'll definitely kill herself

771
00:56:48.256 --> 00:56:50.325
Can't you even imagine that?

772
00:56:55.094 --> 00:56:56.466
There's a way

773
00:56:59.849 --> 00:57:01.693
It needs a lot of work though..

774
00:57:07.246 --> 00:57:09.316
Are you really sure that it will save Misa

775
00:57:09.351 --> 00:57:12.064
if only I follow your direction

776
00:57:12.246 --> 00:57:14.187
Can't you trust me even a little?

777
00:57:14.222 --> 00:57:17.648
He's smarter than you think

778
00:57:18.256 --> 00:57:20.439
Ok. I trust you

779
00:57:21.256 --> 00:57:22.672
Yagami Light

780
00:57:23.284 --> 00:57:24.931
I leave Misa to you

781
00:57:33.236 --> 00:57:36.014
What are you doing with my Death Note?

782
00:57:36.412 --> 00:57:37.939
I'm just hiding it

783
00:57:38.855 --> 00:57:42.529
When I discard its possession. I'll say...

784
00:57:44.067 --> 00:57:45.393
"I discard it"

785
00:57:47.250 --> 00:57:49.928
"I discard it"...
hum....

786
00:57:52.266 --> 00:57:54.266
Hey stalker

787
00:57:54.301 --> 00:57:56.266
If you quit now.

788
00:57:56.301 --> 00:57:58.349
I won't accuse you!

789
00:58:00.014 --> 00:58:03.090
I'll give you my autograph and a kiss!

790
00:58:04.936 --> 00:58:06.936
Oh please!

791
00:58:06.246 --> 00:58:08.246
Let me out of here!

792
00:58:09.402 --> 00:58:11.031
What happened to her during the blackout

793
00:58:11.066 --> 00:58:12.031
She kept repeating..

794
00:58:14.576 --> 00:58:17.123
We are not stalkers.

795
00:58:17.158 --> 00:58:18.095
We are the police

796
00:58:18.918 --> 00:58:21.928
The police can't do such a thing!

797
00:58:21.963 --> 00:58:24.928
Pop stars are wiser than you think!

798
00:58:24.963 --> 00:58:26.928
If you think we are stalkers.

799
00:58:26.963 --> 00:58:28.928
why did you keep silent?

800
00:58:28.963 --> 00:58:30.857
I don't know!

801
00:58:30.938 --> 00:58:32.938
You suddenly caught me

802
00:58:32.973 --> 00:58:35.938
when I was just going to have lunch with Light

803
00:58:36.710 --> 00:58:38.949
Do you admit the relationship between Yagmai Light?

804
00:58:38.984 --> 00:58:39.908
Of course...

805
00:58:39.943 --> 00:58:41.983
Of course I do. He's my boyfriend.

806
00:58:43.587 --> 00:58:45.632
Is she really the same person?

807
00:58:46.398 --> 00:58:48.550
Then how. did you and Light know each other?

808
00:58:48.585 --> 00:58:52.072
I fell in love with him at first sight at Sakura TV station

809
00:58:52.583 --> 00:58:55.217
I found his address and went to his home

810
00:58:56.971 --> 00:58:58.102
Anything wrong?

811
00:59:00.773 --> 00:59:02.659
You know how she acted before

812
00:59:03.512 --> 00:59:06.041
Now she frankly admitted about Light

813
00:59:06.751 --> 00:59:07.756
I'm confused

814
00:59:16.277 --> 00:59:18.746
Who said that we can't bring cellphones into the office?

815
00:59:18.781 --> 00:59:19.577
ya..

816
00:59:20.312 --> 00:59:21.225
Hello

817
00:59:23.414 --> 00:59:25.203
I got it. please come in

818
00:59:26.713 --> 00:59:30.426
Keep recording and shut down the screen

819
00:59:30.461 --> 00:59:30.898
Yes

820
00:59:35.894 --> 00:59:37.864
Is someone coming?

821
00:59:39.948 --> 00:59:42.016
Light!

822
00:59:44.826 --> 00:59:46.765
I've told Ryuzaki but...

823
00:59:48.395 --> 00:59:50.395
As L said. I might be the Kira

824
00:59:51.070 --> 00:59:52.797
What on earth are you talking about?

825
00:59:53.928 --> 00:59:55.820
I've been thinking that..

826
00:59:56.873 --> 01:00:00.034
It may be better if people who committed serious crimes die

827
01:00:00.879 --> 01:00:02.169
So it's possible that I may become Kira

828
01:00:02.170 --> 01:00:04.975
You're not the only one who thinks so!

829
01:00:05.089 --> 01:00:06.612
Are you trying to cover Misa?

830
01:00:07.624 --> 01:00:12.254
I don't know much about her yet since we've just started dating

831
01:00:12.628 --> 01:00:14.624
I can't believe that she's Kira

832
01:00:15.456 --> 01:00:17.376
Of course. I'm not conscious of Kira in me

833
01:00:17.377 --> 01:00:18.713
but.

834
01:00:19.511 --> 01:00:21.565
I might have a multiple personality

835
01:00:22.709 --> 01:00:23.935
I want you to figure it out

836
01:00:23.936 --> 01:00:26.364
We investigated you. but couldn't find anything suspicious

837
01:00:26.947 --> 01:00:29.265
But we watched over him only when he was home

838
01:00:29.786 --> 01:00:32.474
We don't know exactly what he did outside

839
01:00:33.072 --> 01:00:36.745
Then tie his arms and legs and keep him under surveillance

840
01:00:36.780 --> 01:00:37.657
This time

841
01:00:39.394 --> 01:00:41.671
It's an around-the-clock surveillance

842
01:00:43.041 --> 01:00:44.655
That'll be fine with me

843
01:00:45.687 --> 01:00:47.243
But if.

844
01:00:47.734 --> 01:00:50.773
new crimes are committed while I'm under surveillance...

845
01:00:51.211 --> 01:00:53.111
and Kira punishes the criminals

846
01:00:53.957 --> 01:00:55.073
When it happens

847
01:00:55.736 --> 01:00:57.875
We'll certainly free you

848
01:01:00.834 --> 01:01:01.677
Thank you

849
01:01:10.154 --> 01:01:10.760
Light...

850
01:01:12.355 --> 01:01:13.471
Do you really mean it?

851
01:01:34.120 --> 01:01:36.351
Where's Light?

852
01:01:38.124 --> 01:01:40.529
What happened to our son?

853
01:01:41.127 --> 01:01:43.109
Dad. why don't you say something?

854
01:01:43.129 --> 01:01:44.409
Dear

855
01:02:35.115 --> 01:02:37.848
"Celebrating LIght's 18th birthday"

856
01:02:39.687 --> 01:02:43.352
"This is a rulebook which was based on human wisdom"

857
01:02:43.387 --> 01:02:46.020
"which still struggles to answer what justice is"

858
01:02:46.425 --> 01:02:47.489
"Thanks. dad!"

859
01:02:48.128 --> 01:02:50.111
"I want to study and think about what justice is"

860
01:02:55.135 --> 01:03:00.159
Amane Misa: Surveillance Day 8

861
01:03:01.631 --> 01:03:02.634
Yagami Light: Surveillance Day 3

862
01:03:04.964 --> 01:03:06.419
How is it. Ryuzaki?

863
01:03:08.114 --> 01:03:10.662
Has kira killed anyone yet?

864
01:03:12.749 --> 01:03:15.789
There's no activities so far

865
01:03:17.439 --> 01:03:19.515
No criminals have been killed

866
01:03:20.697 --> 01:03:21.774
Is that so...

867
01:03:24.130 --> 01:03:27.518
Then I'm getting even more suspicious.

868
01:03:28.597 --> 01:03:30.712
I'm soooo bored!

869
01:03:31.137 --> 01:03:32.700
I can't eat apples

870
01:03:33.139 --> 01:03:35.305
and I can't even talk with you.

871
01:03:36.142 --> 01:03:38.871
I wonder how Rem's doing now

872
01:04:15.114 --> 01:04:18.886
Where's my ID card?

873
01:04:19.667 --> 01:04:21.151
Does anyone know?

874
01:05:00.556 --> 01:05:02.169
Don't make a sound

875
01:05:02.887 --> 01:05:05.567
I brought a little gift for you

876
01:05:09.135 --> 01:05:11.137
Misa. Day 12
Light: Day 7

877
01:05:11.172 --> 01:05:13.105
I want to see Light

878
01:05:14.140 --> 01:05:16.142
I want to see Light. stalkers!

879
01:05:16.177 --> 01:05:18.076
Dad. mom

880
01:05:20.113 --> 01:05:21.166
Light.

881
01:05:21.589 --> 01:05:23.382
You look exhausted

882
01:05:25.610 --> 01:05:26.870
Are you okay?

883
01:05:29.122 --> 01:05:31.697
Yeah. I know I look so miserable right now

884
01:05:33.126 --> 01:05:35.850
But I don't care about such as useless pride..

885
01:05:38.086 --> 01:05:38.805
"I discard it"

886
01:05:40.133 --> 01:05:42.200
You "discard" it?

887
01:05:42.822 --> 01:05:44.926
You'll lose your memory

888
01:05:45.138 --> 01:05:47.106
Alright. Light.

889
01:05:48.141 --> 01:05:50.075
Goodbye

890
01:06:12.957 --> 01:06:13.779
Ryuzaki...

891
01:06:15.591 --> 01:06:16.436
What's wrong?

892
01:06:18.137 --> 01:06:21.124
I know I asked you to do this to me

893
01:06:22.141 --> 01:06:24.083
But now I surely know..

894
01:06:26.022 --> 01:06:27.426
This is a waste of time

895
01:06:28.776 --> 01:06:30.347
I'm not Kira

896
01:06:31.106 --> 01:06:34.237
I'll be the judge of that. not you

897
01:06:35.300 --> 01:06:37.302
It's totally impossible to do such cruel things

898
01:06:37.337 --> 01:06:39.097
without being conscious

899
01:06:40.708 --> 01:06:41.635
Don't you think so?

900
01:06:42.775 --> 01:06:45.418
It was you who said that you might be Kira

901
01:06:46.153 --> 01:06:47.972
without being conscious

902
01:06:48.313 --> 01:06:50.306
While I'm here. I clearly saw my goal

903
01:06:51.016 --> 01:06:53.806
I won't let Kira go free. he drove me into a corner

904
01:06:54.319 --> 01:06:55.527
Ryuzaki!

905
01:06:55.528 --> 01:06:58.372
Let's cooperate and find a way to reach Kira!

906
01:06:59.000 --> 01:07:02.747
We can get him!

907
01:07:03.920 --> 01:07:07.091
Light...
suddenly became so positive

908
01:07:24.316 --> 01:07:26.873
Misa: Day 19
Light: Day 14

909
01:07:27.094 --> 01:07:29.790
Since he offered to do it. but

910
01:07:30.474 --> 01:07:32.126
I'm worried about Misa

911
01:07:36.480 --> 01:07:37.921
She's a tough kid

912
01:07:38.482 --> 01:07:40.353
If I were her. I'd go insane

913
01:07:48.327 --> 01:07:48.930
Ryuzaki!

914
01:07:50.666 --> 01:07:51.614
Kira is back!

915
01:07:52.668 --> 01:07:54.960
Criminals are dying of heart attack one after another

916
01:07:57.673 --> 01:07:58.232
Light!

917
01:07:59.228 --> 01:08:01.976
There's been no action from Kira for 2 weeks.

918
01:08:03.230 --> 01:08:04.460
It's time you admit that you're Kira

919
01:08:04.495 --> 01:08:05.178
Hey!

920
01:08:07.297 --> 01:08:10.589
If you see only the current situation. I'm guilty. But this is a trap...

921
01:08:12.128 --> 01:08:14.679
I said I'm not Kira!
Believe me!

922
01:08:38.907 --> 01:08:41.454
Why did Kira... choose me as his replacement?

923
01:08:42.651 --> 01:08:46.529
You often predicted who'll be the next target of Kira

924
01:08:47.619 --> 01:08:50.759
You must have noticed the reason through your reports

925
01:08:58.967 --> 01:09:00.969
Kira's punishment...

926
01:09:01.004 --> 01:09:03.972
...is nearly the same as my view on justice

927
01:09:04.478 --> 01:09:05.557
That's what I thought

928
01:09:12.795 --> 01:09:15.403
Kira is just trying to make the world a better place

929
01:09:15.950 --> 01:09:19.350
It's my mission to tell the people that he's doing the right thing

930
01:09:20.260 --> 01:09:22.861
If I were Kira. I would use the media more efficiently!

931
01:09:23.958 --> 01:09:28.982
That makes you the most suitable person as Kira's partner

932
01:09:29.810 --> 01:09:30.920
That is the reason

933
01:09:31.966 --> 01:09:33.995
Kira chose me as his partner...

934
01:09:45.947 --> 01:09:49.906
Misa: Day 23
Light: Day 18

935
01:09:51.966 --> 01:09:55.516
Criminals are constantly being killed

936
01:09:56.958 --> 01:09:58.960
Even the ones they never knew

937
01:09:58.995 --> 01:10:02.782
It's impossible to kill them in this situation

938
01:10:05.967 --> 01:10:07.383
For example.

939
01:10:08.090 --> 01:10:09.966
if the Kira's ability has been transferred to another person

940
01:10:10.788 --> 01:10:12.731
and the person has become the Third Kira

941
01:10:13.296 --> 01:10:15.754
and they've lost their memories

942
01:10:15.977 --> 01:10:17.612
It explains everything

943
01:10:18.456 --> 01:10:19.287
Even if you were right.

944
01:10:19.929 --> 01:10:21.562
there's no way to prove it

945
01:10:27.666 --> 01:10:28.434
Ryuzaki

946
01:10:31.708 --> 01:10:34.273
Why don't we try a different approach?

947
01:10:51.177 --> 01:10:52.942
How do you feel?

948
01:10:56.182 --> 01:10:57.932
Good. thanks

949
01:10:58.184 --> 01:11:00.091
I'm impressed with your courage

950
01:11:02.188 --> 01:11:05.509
Still. we have the evidence found in Amane's room

951
01:11:06.116 --> 01:11:10.429
You can't go outside until we solve the case

952
01:11:11.197 --> 01:11:13.002
If I have to stay here anyway

953
01:11:14.063 --> 01:11:16.953
Let me go back to the team and help you find Kira

954
01:11:17.203 --> 01:11:20.690
Yes. I was thinking about the exact same thing

955
01:11:21.743 --> 01:11:26.838
You have to stay with me all day and assist me

956
01:11:28.181 --> 01:11:29.581
Thanks. Ryuzaki

957
01:11:30.883 --> 01:11:32.409
Let's find Kira together

958
01:11:41.166 --> 01:11:42.261
I love you...

959
01:11:43.196 --> 01:11:44.720
Light

960
01:11:59.224 --> 01:12:00.926
Ms Wakita!
Are you okay?

961
01:12:00.914 --> 01:12:02.167
What happened to you?

962
01:12:02.852 --> 01:12:03.764
Get an ambulance!

963
01:12:10.189 --> 01:12:11.245
She's dead

964
01:12:12.562 --> 01:12:15.965
Her name is Wakita Masako and she was wanted for

965
01:12:16.195 --> 01:12:18.795
killing her colleague when she was working in a nightclub

966
01:12:19.966 --> 01:12:21.003
Is this another case

967
01:12:21.004 --> 01:12:23.467
of punishment from Kira?

968
01:12:24.203 --> 01:12:30.352
We found Wakita's address and tried to interview her

969
01:12:30.552 --> 01:12:32.344
but she died in front of us

970
01:12:33.096 --> 01:12:35.501
Ms. Takada. you must be shocked

971
01:12:36.182 --> 01:12:38.184
She did not have any health problem

972
01:12:38.219 --> 01:12:42.143
so it is natural to think that she was killed by Kira

973
01:12:43.580 --> 01:12:45.507
Now please look at this graph

974
01:12:46.482 --> 01:12:49.664
This is the result of a poll taken from 1000 people in Japan

975
01:12:50.196 --> 01:12:52.198
According to the result.

976
01:12:52.233 --> 01:12:54.679
60% of them are supporting Kira

977
01:12:54.714 --> 01:12:56.167
This is surprising isn't it?

978
01:12:56.202 --> 01:12:57.538
I don't think so

979
01:12:58.204 --> 01:13:00.206
Considering that the crime rate has been decreasing

980
01:13:03.013 --> 01:13:05.167
by the appearance of Kira. this result is expected

981
01:13:08.181 --> 01:13:10.149
Not bad

982
01:13:11.732 --> 01:13:14.559
This is a fact that Kira is fighting against evil

983
01:13:15.959 --> 01:13:18.136
What is the true justice?

984
01:13:19.082 --> 01:13:21.255
Does the police. or L. really can help us?

985
01:13:22.061 --> 01:13:23.714
Kira is trying to make us thing.

986
01:13:24.197 --> 01:13:25.788
She's good

987
01:13:28.201 --> 01:13:30.221
We can't blame her because

988
01:13:31.469 --> 01:13:34.665
We haven't found any clues to go on

989
01:13:36.209 --> 01:13:38.153
What's wrong Ryuzaki?
It's not like you

990
01:13:39.703 --> 01:13:41.671
Oh. great work!

991
01:13:43.234 --> 01:13:44.247
Thank you for supervising

992
01:13:44.535 --> 01:13:46.022
Your comments were witty

993
01:13:47.974 --> 01:13:48.972
Thank you so much!

994
01:13:50.139 --> 01:13:51.549
The director said that...

995
01:13:52.191 --> 01:13:54.095
you'd be a good anchor

996
01:13:54.771 --> 01:13:55.415
Really?

997
01:13:56.217 --> 01:13:59.351
for being critical towards the society through Kira's case...

998
01:13:59.774 --> 01:14:02.907
Your brave. intelligent attitude has attracted the viewers.

999
01:14:04.828 --> 01:14:06.970
You're becoming more attractive

1000
01:14:08.072 --> 01:14:09.059
Mr. Demegawa!

1001
01:14:12.155 --> 01:14:14.151
Could you ask your boss?

1002
01:14:15.161 --> 01:14:17.177
to spray pesticide in the studio

1003
01:14:17.749 --> 01:14:20.145
since a noisy bug's flying around here

1004
01:14:20.766 --> 01:14:21.915
Saeko!

1005
01:14:22.188 --> 01:14:23.520
Let's go have dinner?

1006
01:14:26.037 --> 01:14:26.866
Kiyomi

1007
01:14:27.784 --> 01:14:29.870
You know. each employee has an appropriate role. right?

1008
01:14:30.157 --> 01:14:31.496
What is your role. then?

1009
01:14:32.660 --> 01:14:34.953
No one's listening to your trashy comments!

1010
01:14:35.848 --> 01:14:36.573
Let's go

1011
01:14:43.209 --> 01:14:47.239
I say she's too fugly to be the anchor for our show!

1012
01:14:47.748 --> 01:14:48.840
Oh. come on

1013
01:14:49.182 --> 01:14:52.002
We employees can't say no to your boss. you know.

1014
01:14:52.719 --> 01:14:53.964
Are you kidding me?

1015
01:14:54.187 --> 01:14:56.950
You're the one who said no to your boss and showed Kira's video!

1016
01:14:58.035 --> 01:14:59.450
You slept with her. didn't you?

1017
01:15:00.707 --> 01:15:04.027
There's nobody but you who got a job by sleeping with me

1018
01:15:06.012 --> 01:15:06.992
Stop the car

1019
01:15:06.993 --> 01:15:07.961
Huh?

1020
01:15:08.201 --> 01:15:09.628
Stop the car now!

1021
01:15:18.594 --> 01:15:19.953
I'll never forgive her!

1022
01:15:21.203 --> 01:15:21.943
Hey. wait!

1023
01:15:22.932 --> 01:15:23.851
Calm down!

1024
01:15:25.365 --> 01:15:26.587
What's the matter with you!

1025
01:15:30.548 --> 01:15:32.723
You can't catch a taxi here!

1026
01:15:48.746 --> 01:15:49.840
Good evening

1027
01:15:53.179 --> 01:15:54.042
Good evening

1028
01:15:54.489 --> 01:15:57.862
Welcome to Evening Spot.
I'm Takada Kiyomi. the new anchor

1029
01:15:59.657 --> 01:16:00.599
First of all.

1030
01:16:01.187 --> 01:16:03.883
I have to announce a sad news

1031
01:16:05.695 --> 01:16:09.699
Last night. Nishiyama Saeko. our excellent former anchor.

1032
01:16:09.195 --> 01:16:11.760
died of a car accident

1033
01:16:13.199 --> 01:16:15.167
She was. for me..

1034
01:16:16.202 --> 01:16:17.814
a few years senior than me

1035
01:16:18.204 --> 01:16:21.625
and one of the person I respected the most

1036
01:16:23.617 --> 01:16:26.586
It is very sad that...

1037
01:16:27.179 --> 01:16:29.547
my first job as an anchor is

1038
01:16:31.039 --> 01:16:32.750
to announce about Saeko's death

1039
01:16:37.541 --> 01:16:40.187
This feels like being on a honeymoon!

1040
01:16:42.194 --> 01:16:45.197
If I can always spend my time with you like this

1041
01:16:45.232 --> 01:16:47.313
I won't want to go back to work

1042
01:16:50.202 --> 01:16:55.260
But. if they lock me up again. I'll die!

1043
01:16:56.859 --> 01:16:57.665
Oh. sorry!

1044
01:17:02.181 --> 01:17:03.534
Light

1045
01:17:04.183 --> 01:17:04.823
Are you studying?

1046
01:17:04.858 --> 01:17:07.236
Sorry Misa. can you please leave me alone for a while?

1047
01:17:25.609 --> 01:17:26.620
I'll go downstairs

1048
01:17:27.553 --> 01:17:28.528
Dont leave me alone

1049
01:17:34.702 --> 01:17:36.662
Light. come back soon. okay?

1050
01:17:37.183 --> 01:17:39.985
I'm sorry. but I'll set you free soon

1051
01:17:54.577 --> 01:17:56.445
Ryuzaki is a little depressed

1052
01:17:57.133 --> 01:17:59.613
Yeah. because he lost all his clues...

1053
01:18:01.669 --> 01:18:03.097
You're too loud

1054
01:18:03.209 --> 01:18:04.460
Ryuzaki!

1055
01:18:05.177 --> 01:18:06.190
Please be honest

1056
01:18:06.648 --> 01:18:08.782
What is the percentage that I'm Kira?

1057
01:18:10.182 --> 01:18:13.302
The percentage that you are Kira is...

1058
01:18:14.073 --> 01:18:15.063
nearly zero

1059
01:18:15.971 --> 01:18:16.449
I see

1060
01:18:18.190 --> 01:18:18.931
Great

1061
01:18:19.575 --> 01:18:20.326
I'm so happy

1062
01:18:21.193 --> 01:18:25.197
I'm also happy that you don't seem to be Kira. but

1063
01:18:26.363 --> 01:18:28.706
at the same time I lost all the clues

1064
01:18:30.157 --> 01:18:31.784
There's a vital clue

1065
01:18:32.751 --> 01:18:33.634
What if I said so?

1066
01:18:35.305 --> 01:18:36.864
When will you come back?

1067
01:18:37.209 --> 01:18:38.395
Are you serious?

1068
01:18:39.178 --> 01:18:40.030
Look at this

1069
01:18:44.183 --> 01:18:46.849
The red one is Kira's action before I was confined

1070
01:18:47.568 --> 01:18:48.871
and the blue one is his new action.

1071
01:18:48.187 --> 01:18:52.038
I profiled them statistically

1072
01:18:52.191 --> 01:18:55.189
Are these the same person?

1073
01:18:55.194 --> 01:18:56.178
No

1074
01:18:56.514 --> 01:18:58.189
They have some differences

1075
01:19:04.575 --> 01:19:05.772
Oh. they really do!

1076
01:19:07.206 --> 01:19:10.209
Even if you try to imitate someone's movement

1077
01:19:10.244 --> 01:19:12.127
you can't hide your habits or personality

1078
01:19:13.143 --> 01:19:15.680
They appear to be a remarkable tendency

1079
01:19:16.182 --> 01:19:17.359
Ryuzaki...

1080
01:19:18.059 --> 01:19:19.217
He's got the energy again!

1081
01:19:19.412 --> 01:19:20.347
I bet you know it

1082
01:19:21.463 --> 01:19:24.400
If Kira before and after the restraint were the same person

1083
01:19:24.435 --> 01:19:26.674
THe distribution wouldn't be so different

1084
01:19:27.819 --> 01:19:30.127
It means that they are different person and

1085
01:19:30.196 --> 01:19:32.802
we can see the distinct characterists that show their tendencies

1086
01:19:34.200 --> 01:19:35.145
How is it . Ryuzaki?

1087
01:19:36.160 --> 01:19:36.918
Doesn't it give you some motivation?

1088
01:19:38.039 --> 01:19:40.000
Yes Light. that you so much

1089
01:19:41.460 --> 01:19:42.703
By the way. what are the characteristics?

1090
01:19:43.923 --> 01:19:46.658
Well. the first characteristic is publicity

1091
01:19:46.892 --> 01:19:51.521
I mean. the new Kira cares slightly more about cases featured by the media

1092
01:19:52.455 --> 01:19:54.128
And the second factor is

1093
01:19:54.163 --> 01:19:55.706
gender

1094
01:19:55.901 --> 01:20:00.543
The new one focuses on more cases related to women

1095
01:20:01.444 --> 01:20:03.022
This Kira may be a woman

1096
01:20:03.725 --> 01:20:05.194
And the third factor is...

1097
01:20:06.612 --> 01:20:09.085
which might be the answer already

1098
01:20:09.615 --> 01:20:10.945
What? Oh come one Light. tell us

1099
01:20:11.119 --> 01:20:14.451
frequency of the cases reported by one broadcasting company

1100
01:20:15.296 --> 01:20:16.994
Which company?

1101
01:20:18.591 --> 01:20:19.783
It's Sakura TV

1102
01:20:23.810 --> 01:20:25.598
To sum up

1103
01:20:26.468 --> 01:20:29.561
compared to the First Kira. this new Kira is

1104
01:20:30.280 --> 01:20:35.471
more media-oriented. feminine. and Sakura TV...

1105
01:20:37.829 --> 01:20:40.872
The anchor died of accident and the new one is female!

1106
01:21:52.348 --> 01:21:55.385
Does she keep a diary in such an old notebook?

1107
01:21:52.348 --> 01:21:54.004
That's not snobbish people do

1108
01:21:54.403 --> 01:21:55.695
She must have a lot of money

1109
01:21:56.148 --> 01:21:59.877
I don't think it's a diary. SHe's copying down from the PC screen

1110
01:22:01.058 --> 01:22:02.878
Can you zoom in the surface of the notebook?

1111
01:22:02.913 --> 01:22:04.563
Okay. wait a second

1112
01:22:16.595 --> 01:22:17.560
What are these��

1113
01:22:19.117 --> 01:22:22.819
Names of the criminals who've just been killed by Kira

1114
01:22:22.854 --> 01:22:27.275
Ms. Sagami. capture them and confirm that they are

1115
01:22:27.979 --> 01:22:28.863
Yes

1116
01:22:31.590 --> 01:22:34.561
Killing one after another everyday

1117
01:22:35.000 --> 01:22:37.594
Are there any left to kill?

1118
01:22:38.496 --> 01:22:40.790
It tells you how sinful human beings are

1119
01:22:41.959 --> 01:22:44.517
Look who's talking

1120
01:22:44.552 --> 01:22:45.536
I know

1121
01:22:46.483 --> 01:22:48.685
Punishing the sinful people. I'm even more sinful

1122
01:22:49.822 --> 01:22:52.392
But even those sins burden me for my entire life

1123
01:22:52.718 --> 01:22:54.147
I have to fulfill my duty

1124
01:22:55.209 --> 01:22:56.197
Is she talking to herself?

1125
01:22:56.373 --> 01:22:56.943
No.

1126
01:22:57.788 --> 01:22:59.375
She's definitely talking to someone else

1127
01:23:05.133 --> 01:23:06.355
It's confirmed

1128
01:23:07.492 --> 01:23:09.745
Names of the left page belong to the criminals

1129
01:23:10.596 --> 01:23:13.010
who died of heart attack yesterday

1130
01:23:13.751 --> 01:23:15.306
Accurate details of when and how they died..

1131
01:23:14.600 --> 01:23:17.789
including the unannounced cases

1132
01:23:18.451 --> 01:23:19.848
We got it!

1133
01:23:20.399 --> 01:23:22.450
Boss! Let me arrest her!

1134
01:23:22.624 --> 01:23:25.705
She can make an excuse that she was just researching their deaths

1135
01:23:27.027 --> 01:23:28.054
You're right...

1136
01:23:28.268 --> 01:23:28.971
One more thing

1137
01:23:29.919 --> 01:23:33.109
What she's writing down on the right page now..

1138
01:23:33.466 --> 01:23:35.158
are also names of the criminals

1139
01:23:36.135 --> 01:23:38.067
but they are still alive

1140
01:23:40.123 --> 01:23:42.475
They must be the next targets

1141
01:23:43.773 --> 01:23:46.612
If they really die tomorrow. we can conclude that she's Kira

1142
01:23:47.354 --> 01:23:50.740
or she has some kind of relationship with Kira

1143
01:23:51.353 --> 01:23:53.408
We can't just wait until those people die!

1144
01:23:54.395 --> 01:23:56.125
Damn it. what should we do!

1145
01:23:56.633 --> 01:23:58.175
We can use Kira's cruelty

1146
01:24:01.192 --> 01:24:02.675
Hello. Ms. Takada

1147
01:24:03.640 --> 01:24:07.554
You keep getting scoops about Kira as a supporter

1148
01:24:08.846 --> 01:24:11.484
I found out the reasons

1149
01:24:11.849 --> 01:24:13.049
What do you mean?

1150
01:24:13.817 --> 01:24:16.214
I peeked in your room

1151
01:24:17.821 --> 01:24:19.192
It's illegal!

1152
01:24:19.227 --> 01:24:22.572
Every secret is hidden in your black notebook. right?

1153
01:24:23.151 --> 01:24:24.915
I want you to buy the tapes

1154
01:24:25.633 --> 01:24:26.575
for 5 million yen

1155
01:25:07.381 --> 01:25:09.383
All the names she wrote down yesterday...

1156
01:25:09.603 --> 01:25:11.614
matches the criminals who died today.

1157
01:25:12.141 --> 01:25:13.908
Takada Kiyomi is the Kira!

1158
01:25:14.143 --> 01:25:15.271
She definitely is!

1159
01:25:26.122 --> 01:25:27.275
I'm the one who called you

1160
01:25:34.422 --> 01:25:35.412
"Miatsuo Yosuke"

1161
01:25:35.447 --> 01:25:39.721
If I die. the tapes will automatically go public

1162
01:25:40.461 --> 01:25:43.464
Are you doing this with someone else?

1163
01:25:43.139 --> 01:25:44.734
No. I'm alone

1164
01:25:47.898 --> 01:25:50.863
There's my account number on the back of the card

1165
01:25:51.147 --> 01:25:54.123
Transfer 5 million yen to my account

1166
01:25:55.117 --> 01:25:57.119
Once payment is confirmed

1167
01:25:57.154 --> 01:25:58.832
I'll give you the tapes

1168
01:26:00.122 --> 01:26:01.588
Thank you

1169
01:26:07.460 --> 01:26:10.198
It's me. Kiyomi. turn on the TV

1170
01:26:10.428 --> 01:26:11.440
Sakura TV

1171
01:26:12.134 --> 01:26:13.091
Why?

1172
01:26:13.633 --> 01:26:15.247
No reason. just turn on the TV

1173
01:26:21.234 --> 01:26:23.590
Kira is a woman?

1174
01:26:24.146 --> 01:26:26.617
Wow. I couldn't think of it

1175
01:26:26.855 --> 01:26:27.574
"Special Program: Chasing Kira's Identity"

1176
01:26:28.007 --> 01:26:30.307
I have the tapes as evidence

1177
01:26:30.515 --> 01:26:32.989
Wait. It's too soon to show them

1178
01:26:34.123 --> 01:26:36.987
We'll show you the videos at the end of the program

1179
01:26:38.127 --> 01:26:39.775
You'll see Kira's identity

1180
01:26:40.948 --> 01:26:43.503
1 hour 25 minutes and 40 seconds left

1181
01:26:44.133 --> 01:26:46.543
until then. we'll ask our guests some more questions

1182
01:26:46.578 --> 01:26:48.816
We were scooped by other guys

1183
01:26:49.749 --> 01:26:52.075
I'm sorry...
I'll call you back

1184
01:26:53.142 --> 01:26:54.078
"that female..."

1185
01:26:57.748 --> 01:26:58.955
I did it as you said

1186
01:26:59.999 --> 01:27:01.014
You're a good actor

1187
01:27:10.063 --> 01:27:11.077
Now. what do we do next?

1188
01:27:16.707 --> 01:27:19.137
"Matsuo Yosuke suicide"

1189
01:27:20.135 --> 01:27:22.727
22:36. refuses to appear on the program

1190
01:27:25.161 --> 01:27:28.731
after cleaning out all the evidences he has

1191
01:27:29.617 --> 01:27:32.039
jumps from the roof of the building

1192
01:27:34.707 --> 01:27:36.177
she's writing down how he's going to die

1193
01:27:37.119 --> 01:27:39.602
Kira can control the action of the people she's going to kill!

1194
01:27:41.899 --> 01:27:43.488
It's safe. Rem

1195
01:27:45.029 --> 01:27:46.022
"Now it's safe"

1196
01:27:47.500 --> 01:27:48.522
what is she talking about?

1197
01:27:49.581 --> 01:27:54.824
Does she really believe that Matsuda will act according to what she's written?

1198
01:27:59.396 --> 01:28:03.431
Are you for or against Kira's actions?

1199
01:28:04.291 --> 01:28:05.248
Don't you see?

1200
01:28:05.927 --> 01:28:08.562
If I supported Kira. I wouldn't appear on TV like this

1201
01:28:09.830 --> 01:28:11.136
Don't you think it's dangerous?

1202
01:28:11.171 --> 01:28:12.475
It's a minute past the time....

1203
01:28:13.031 --> 01:28:14.118
Rem. what's going on?

1204
01:28:15.641 --> 01:28:16.152
"Rem.."

1205
01:28:17.757 --> 01:28:19.058
What is "Rem"?

1206
01:28:19.474 --> 01:28:20.160
Who is she talking to?

1207
01:28:24.385 --> 01:28:25.636
A Death God?

1208
01:28:28.116 --> 01:28:31.671
"Matsuo Yosuke"
It must be a false name!

1209
01:28:32.572 --> 01:28:35.153
Rem! You must've known it since you're the Death God!

1210
01:28:35.188 --> 01:28:37.112
You didn't tell me!

1211
01:28:37.854 --> 01:28:41.327
She often says "Death God"

1212
01:28:41.362 --> 01:28:42.852
Is it a code or something?

1213
01:28:44.119 --> 01:28:46.087
The most logical way is to think that

1214
01:28:47.515 --> 01:28:48.888
the Death God exists

1215
01:28:50.040 --> 01:28:50.699
What?

1216
01:28:51.712 --> 01:28:51.992
Okay

1217
01:28:53.594 --> 01:28:54.383
Let's make a deal

1218
01:28:55.739 --> 01:28:56.739
Give me the Death God's eyes!

1219
01:29:01.722 --> 01:29:03.840
The Death God's eyes...?

1220
01:29:07.480 --> 01:29:09.047
The Second Kira said the same thing

1221
01:29:10.731 --> 01:29:12.712
The Second Kira has the ability to kill only by the faces

1222
01:29:14.500 --> 01:29:15.953
That's "the Death God's eye"

1223
01:30:30.391 --> 01:30:30.855
Roll down the window

1224
01:30:36.722 --> 01:30:37.615
Show me your ID

1225
01:30:39.912 --> 01:30:40.741
You don't have it?

1226
01:30:42.353 --> 01:30:45.056
Don't look at me like that. the rule is the rule

1227
01:30:46.708 --> 01:30:48.754
Shidohara Genta

1228
01:30:50.725 --> 01:30:51.681
How did you know my name?

1229
01:30:55.861 --> 01:30:56.629
Wait!

1230
01:30:57.665 --> 01:30:59.644
Do you appear on TV?

1231
01:31:01.352 --> 01:31:02.855
Something TV...

1232
01:31:03.867 --> 01:31:05.022
You're an anchor. right?

1233
01:31:06.395 --> 01:31:07.296
What are you doing?

1234
01:31:07.975 --> 01:31:08.898
Wait!

1235
01:31:43.059 --> 01:31:46.146
A policeman fell down. but I can't help him!

1236
01:31:46.873 --> 01:31:47.534
Got it

1237
01:31:48.875 --> 01:31:49.680
Did she use "the eye"?

1238
01:31:50.727 --> 01:31:52.554
It's too dangerous to let her go any further

1239
01:31:53.526 --> 01:31:57.917
We don't know how she did it. but it's better to catch her

1240
01:32:50.389 --> 01:32:51.530
Freeze!

1241
01:32:57.758 --> 01:32:59.060
Let me go!

1242
01:33:13.024 --> 01:33:13.741
Let me go!

1243
01:33:21.789 --> 01:33:25.278
We have watched every single action you made

1244
01:33:27.520 --> 01:33:29.685
The TV program was a fake

1245
01:33:31.356 --> 01:33:32.162
It was a trap!

1246
01:33:32.524 --> 01:33:33.429
Takada Kiyomi!

1247
01:33:35.458 --> 01:33:36.999
How did you do that?

1248
01:33:38.530 --> 01:33:39.693
Are you a detective?

1249
01:33:40.000 --> 01:33:40.477
As Kira..

1250
01:33:41.690 --> 01:33:43.063
How did you kill those people?

1251
01:33:45.504 --> 01:33:47.282
You wrote the names on the notebook

1252
01:33:52.511 --> 01:33:55.060
After writing them down.. what did you do?

1253
01:33:57.316 --> 01:33:58.145
I just write them down

1254
01:33:58.517 --> 01:34:00.050
I said what did you do after!

1255
01:34:02.520 --> 01:34:03.804
Then why don't you try it?

1256
01:34:09.528 --> 01:34:11.530
You write names down and...

1257
01:34:12.033 --> 01:34:13.383
the person whose name is written dies

1258
01:34:14.206 --> 01:34:15.179
The notebook of the Death God

1259
01:34:28.934 --> 01:34:30.858
What the...

1260
01:34:32.518 --> 01:34:33.925
Dad. what's wrong?

1261
01:34:43.529 --> 01:34:46.340
When you touch it. you can see the Death God?

1262
01:34:54.293 --> 01:34:56.154
Ryuzaki. let me touch it!

1263
01:35:12.711 --> 01:35:14.802
Light... are you okay?

1264
01:35:16.528 --> 01:35:18.496
yeah

1265
01:35:23.411 --> 01:35:24.173
I won!

1266
01:35:25.092 --> 01:35:26.569
Everything's under control

1267
01:35:30.509 --> 01:35:34.783
If only I touch the Death Note. my memory will come back

1268
01:35:35.514 --> 01:35:36.473
Is this really true?

1269
01:35:37.243 --> 01:35:37.888
Yes. but

1270
01:35:38.423 --> 01:35:42.177
you can remember it only when you touch the Death Note

1271
01:35:42.212 --> 01:35:45.547
if the Note wasn't the one you used before

1272
01:35:45.735 --> 01:35:50.012
But if I keep the ownership. the memory won't be lost right?

1273
01:35:51.835 --> 01:35:53.414
How can I keep the ownership?

1274
01:35:53.499 --> 01:35:57.751
While you have the memory. kill the former owner

1275
01:35:58.401 --> 01:36:01.367
Good.
That explanation is enough

1276
01:36:02.094 --> 01:36:02.811
Rem

1277
01:36:03.343 --> 01:36:05.311
Give this to the Third Kira

1278
01:36:06.202 --> 01:36:08.545
If you're the Death God. you can find a suitable one

1279
01:36:09.263 --> 01:36:13.189
And after 13 days. let that person resume Kira's job

1280
01:36:13.843 --> 01:36:15.280
I can choose anyone?

1281
01:36:16.306 --> 01:36:20.958
As you won't remember. you can't reach the new owner

1282
01:36:21.771 --> 01:36:24.599
I know about my ability more than anyone else

1283
01:36:25.531 --> 01:36:28.521
I will definitely try hard to find the new Kira

1284
01:36:28.994 --> 01:36:30.013
and catch the person!

1285
01:36:31.172 --> 01:36:34.823
I'll touch the Note before L. or at the same time

1286
01:36:36.508 --> 01:36:37.502
And one more thing

1287
01:36:38.510 --> 01:36:41.007
I have something I want you to write down on the Note

1288
01:36:41.513 --> 01:36:42.731
What is it?

1289
01:36:44.516 --> 01:36:45.545
I've made up

1290
01:36:47.458 --> 01:36:49.124
a false rule of the Death Note

1291
01:37:02.271 --> 01:37:03.844
The Death God exists

1292
01:37:03.879 --> 01:37:05.249
That explains everything

1293
01:37:05.446 --> 01:37:08.138
Now I know how they kill

1294
01:37:09.092 --> 01:37:10.699
If you write down a person's name on the notebook

1295
01:37:11.511 --> 01:37:13.139
that person dies!

1296
01:37:14.301 --> 01:37:15.841
Is this correct. Takada Kiyomi?

1297
01:37:18.517 --> 01:37:21.495
The Death God...
The killer notebook...

1298
01:37:22.521 --> 01:37:25.422
Who will believe this?

1299
01:37:26.220 --> 01:37:29.002
We can't judge her with the current laws!

1300
01:37:29.528 --> 01:37:30.590
That's right

1301
01:37:30.824 --> 01:37:32.543
I didn't kill anybody

1302
01:37:33.437 --> 01:37:35.072
I just wrote down the names

1303
01:37:35.980 --> 01:37:36.431
No

1304
01:37:37.563 --> 01:37:39.906
If we can prove that the notebook kills people

1305
01:37:40.991 --> 01:37:42.132
You'll be guilty

1306
01:37:42.950 --> 01:37:43.627
Death Penalty

1307
01:37:51.516 --> 01:37:53.518
Humans. listen!

1308
01:37:55.062 --> 01:37:57.483
I'm the Death God. Rem

1309
01:37:58.253 --> 01:38:01.162
Only the humans who touched the Death Note can see me

1310
01:38:01.603 --> 01:38:04.297
I can see your lifespan

1311
01:38:05.158 --> 01:38:08.001
And I can take your lives away

1312
01:38:09.501 --> 01:38:13.460
So you'd better not make me angry

1313
01:38:15.114 --> 01:38:18.500
The Death Note has the power of the Death God

1314
01:38:19.511 --> 01:38:21.506
That woman is correct

1315
01:38:21.513 --> 01:38:25.563
the humans whose name is written on the Death Note shall die

1316
01:38:26.193 --> 01:38:27.526
"Takada Kiyomi"

1317
01:38:27.731 --> 01:38:32.038
With so called Death Note you can control the dying situations. can't you?

1318
01:38:34.733 --> 01:38:36.763
Why don't you try it yourself

1319
01:38:37.531 --> 01:38:39.699
by writing her name on the Note?

1320
01:38:40.533 --> 01:38:42.143
Rem. what do you...

1321
01:39:02.130 --> 01:39:02.543
Takada!

1322
01:39:11.056 --> 01:39:11.941
She's dead...

1323
01:39:16.351 --> 01:39:18.354
Light. hand me the notebook

1324
01:39:36.521 --> 01:39:37.848
Overall

1325
01:39:38.390 --> 01:39:40.740
Why did Takada Kiyomi die?

1326
01:39:41.526 --> 01:39:43.945
Accidental heart attack or...

1327
01:39:44.412 --> 01:39:45.129
suicide...?

1328
01:39:46.783 --> 01:39:47.893
Killed by other Kira?

1329
01:39:49.501 --> 01:39:51.469
What do you think. Death God?

1330
01:39:52.117 --> 01:39:53.376
Don't ask me

1331
01:39:56.708 --> 01:40:00.237
The name on the notebook and the dead criminals are the same. but

1332
01:40:00.443 --> 01:40:02.406
there's no name before Light's confinement

1333
01:40:04.516 --> 01:40:05.687
What do you think?

1334
01:40:06.196 --> 01:40:10.420
The owner of the Note might die when the ownership moves to the other

1335
01:40:11.362 --> 01:40:13.373
The First and the Second Kira might have already...

1336
01:40:14.526 --> 01:40:16.172
I see. Now Takada has died

1337
01:40:17.022 --> 01:40:20.238
and the ownership of this notebook has transferred to someone else

1338
01:40:20.589 --> 01:40:21.856
What do you think. Death God?

1339
01:40:22.655 --> 01:40:23.603
Don't ask me

1340
01:40:24.753 --> 01:40:27.127
Who owns the Note now?

1341
01:40:27.987 --> 01:40:28.987
I cannot answer

1342
01:40:30.213 --> 01:40:32.592
Is that the only thing you can say?

1343
01:40:33.244 --> 01:40:34.095
By the way

1344
01:40:36.440 --> 01:40:39.322
about the last rule of this Death Note

1345
01:40:40.566 --> 01:40:45.917
"If the owner does not write any name for 13 days"

1346
01:40:46.617 --> 01:40:47.457
"the owner shall die"

1347
01:40:49.027 --> 01:40:52.986
Considering this rule. the former Kiras have died

1348
01:40:53.543 --> 01:40:56.008
Then Light. who was under surveillance for 18 days?

1349
01:40:56.197 --> 01:41:00.295
and Amane. which was 23 days. are completely innocent

1350
01:41:00.827 --> 01:41:01.906
Death God!

1351
01:41:03.995 --> 01:41:07.460
Are all the rules on this notebook true?

1352
01:41:09.976 --> 01:41:11.673
Yes. they are

1353
01:41:15.109 --> 01:41:18.252
I got it. Light and Misa are free now

1354
01:41:20.056 --> 01:41:22.559
Light. call your mother and go home

1355
01:41:22.594 --> 01:41:23.077
Dad!

1356
01:41:23.531 --> 01:41:26.659
I'd like to stay here and continue working..

1357
01:41:27.566 --> 01:41:28.645
I think I have to

1358
01:41:30.370 --> 01:41:30.926
Ryuzaki

1359
01:41:32.625 --> 01:41:33.881
You need me. don't you?

1360
01:41:35.574 --> 01:41:39.779
I got it.
Light. stay here and help us

1361
01:41:40.766 --> 01:41:42.989
This looks like a common notebook

1362
01:41:43.690 --> 01:41:46.398
I can't believe this thing can kill people

1363
01:41:47.247 --> 01:41:47.933
What?

1364
01:41:48.281 --> 01:41:50.193
Why don't you come with me?

1365
01:41:50.385 --> 01:41:51.813
You can come whenever you want

1366
01:41:52.395 --> 01:41:53.421
Ryuzaki will allow us

1367
01:41:54.113 --> 01:41:55.500
to just talk at the entrance

1368
01:41:56.879 --> 01:41:58.250
Right. I'll come see you everyday

1369
01:41:58.953 --> 01:41:59.693
Be prepared!

1370
01:42:06.558 --> 01:42:07.354
Misa...

1371
01:42:07.913 --> 01:42:08.996
Listen quietly

1372
01:42:12.377 --> 01:42:13.672
Will you do me a favor?

1373
01:42:16.302 --> 01:42:17.372
What is it?

1374
01:42:30.634 --> 01:42:31.614
It's here!

1375
01:43:12.304 --> 01:43:13.991
Light is the Kira...

1376
01:43:16.259 --> 01:43:17.680
He's my God!

1377
01:43:21.057 --> 01:43:22.472
So happy

1378
01:43:23.799 --> 01:43:25.404
My Light is the Kira...!

1379
01:43:28.408 --> 01:43:31.330
I'm back at last!

1380
01:43:33.119 --> 01:43:33.957
Ryuk!

1381
01:43:35.742 --> 01:43:36.842
Why are you here?

1382
01:43:37.744 --> 01:43:39.999
That Death Note is mine

1383
01:43:41.040 --> 01:43:42.986
So this time I'll follow you

1384
01:43:44.293 --> 01:43:47.131
Don't worry. your memory won't be gone

1385
01:43:47.414 --> 01:43:50.788
If you become the owner of this Note

1386
01:43:53.302 --> 01:43:54.740
Okay. I'll be the owner

1387
01:43:56.305 --> 01:43:57.573
Oh. I almost forgot!

1388
01:44:02.311 --> 01:44:03.038
Here

1389
01:44:03.395 --> 01:44:04.395
A gift from Light!

1390
01:44:06.315 --> 01:44:07.664
App.. Apple

1391
01:44:08.008 --> 01:44:10.075
Oh Light... !
He's more generous than he looks!

1392
01:44:13.618 --> 01:44:14.199
"Dear Misa"

1393
01:44:15.291 --> 01:44:20.195
"When you read this letter. you must've remembered everything."

1394
01:44:21.297 --> 01:44:23.809
"To create an ideal world together."

1395
01:44:24.448 --> 01:44:26.979
"You must resume punishing instead of me."

1396
01:44:28.780 --> 01:44:29.472
"And one more thing."

1397
01:44:30.272 --> 01:44:34.704
"do you remember the guy named Ryuzaki I introduced you at my college?"

1398
01:44:35.817 --> 01:44:38.746
"He's our enemy. L"

1399
01:44:40.316 --> 01:44:41.231
That guy is L?

1400
01:44:42.211 --> 01:44:46.147
"You must've seen his real name with your Death God's eye."

1401
01:44:47.290 --> 01:44:49.561
"Write down the name on the Death Note"

1402
01:44:49.932 --> 01:44:51.279
"and eliminate L."

1403
01:44:55.984 --> 01:44:57.382
Elminate L...

1404
01:45:11.313 --> 01:45:11.988
Damn it!

1405
01:45:13.316 --> 01:45:15.174
I can't remember it!

1406
01:45:17.140 --> 01:45:21.076
I saw names of hundreds of people everyday

1407
01:45:22.581 --> 01:45:26.540
Once you discard the ownership. you lose the ability of "the eye"

1408
01:45:27.296 --> 01:45:29.382
I'm sorry. Misa

1409
01:45:32.801 --> 01:45:34.166
Ryuk

1410
01:45:36.521 --> 01:45:38.014
Make the eye-deal again

1411
01:45:38.587 --> 01:45:39.523
Are you sure?

1412
01:45:40.896 --> 01:45:43.009
You've already lost half of your lifespan

1413
01:45:43.683 --> 01:45:45.347
You'll lose the half of if

1414
01:45:45.814 --> 01:45:47.939
I know!

1415
01:45:49.288 --> 01:45:52.172
I don't want to lose my face!

1416
01:45:52.788 --> 01:45:53.328
Face....

1417
01:45:54.781 --> 01:45:56.183
but you have the face.

1418
01:45:56.942 --> 01:45:58.379
Don't take it literally!

1419
01:46:00.467 --> 01:46:02.973
Well. I don't understand human mind really...

1420
01:46:03.419 --> 01:46:05.334
You want the Death God's eye

1421
01:46:09.805 --> 01:46:11.885
I have to obey Light...

1422
01:46:22.667 --> 01:46:24.510
Just one week after Takada's death...

1423
01:46:26.724 --> 01:46:28.327
The new Kira has appeared!

1424
01:46:29.621 --> 01:46:30.858
Criminals are being killed again

1425
01:46:31.577 --> 01:46:34.473
It means there are more notebooks

1426
01:46:35.798 --> 01:46:36.722
Just after.

1427
01:46:38.137 --> 01:46:39.589
Amane Misa was freed

1428
01:46:40.771 --> 01:46:41.361
Ryuzaki!

1429
01:46:42.319 --> 01:46:43.189
Don't give me that again!

1430
01:46:43.434 --> 01:46:45.845
Don't you remember the 13 day rule?

1431
01:46:46.435 --> 01:46:47.073
Mr Yagami

1432
01:46:48.365 --> 01:46:49.164
What?

1433
01:46:49.199 --> 01:46:52.761
Let's inspect this notebook

1434
01:46:54.660 --> 01:46:58.360
I'll ask FBI and have them provide us with two prisoners from the death row

1435
01:46:58.821 --> 01:47:01.163
We'll make the prisoners A write the name of the B

1436
01:47:01.613 --> 01:47:02.613
to see if B will die

1437
01:47:04.684 --> 01:47:08.643
then leave A from the Note for 13 days to see if A will die

1438
01:47:09.798 --> 01:47:13.714
I can't believe you treat human lives like bugs

1439
01:47:14.803 --> 01:47:16.471
It can't be helped

1440
01:47:17.339 --> 01:47:19.601
It's to protect thousands of people's lives

1441
01:47:19.808 --> 01:47:21.029
Isn't there any other way?

1442
01:47:41.781 --> 01:47:42.587
Today. again!

1443
01:47:42.926 --> 01:47:44.951
A numerous number of criminals are killed

1444
01:47:50.806 --> 01:47:51.466
Ryuzaki

1445
01:47:52.415 --> 01:47:54.574
You may be right to stop Kira from killing people

1446
01:47:55.958 --> 01:47:58.617
I'll take responsibility for the experiment

1447
01:47:58.814 --> 01:48:00.245
I'll supervise

1448
01:48:01.554 --> 01:48:02.110
Dad..

1449
01:48:03.260 --> 01:48:05.104
Thank you for understanding

1450
01:48:05.821 --> 01:48:07.642
I'll goto the States

1451
01:48:07.790 --> 01:48:09.157
Are you going alone?

1452
01:48:10.196 --> 01:48:11.561
Let me go with you

1453
01:48:11.794 --> 01:48:12.828
No. you can't

1454
01:48:13.796 --> 01:48:16.236
Stay here with Ryuzaki and wait until I contact you

1455
01:48:17.728 --> 01:48:18.940
I'll be fine

1456
01:48:19.508 --> 01:48:21.693
Others will come with me. little to worry

1457
01:48:22.259 --> 01:48:23.874
Wait. am I worrying?

1458
01:48:26.281 --> 01:48:26.967
How about here?

1459
01:48:27.390 --> 01:48:28.386
Yes. it is worrying

1460
01:48:33.816 --> 01:48:37.772
First. goto the Tokyo Bay heliport by car

1461
01:48:39.609 --> 01:48:44.933
Then fly to the Yokota Camp. The US army will carry you by plane to Washington D.C.

1462
01:48:46.490 --> 01:48:48.030
Watari has arranged for everything

1463
01:48:48.549 --> 01:48:49.153
I got it

1464
01:48:49.798 --> 01:48:51.126
See you later

1465
01:49:19.795 --> 01:49:21.630
Now. we're all alone

1466
01:49:22.798 --> 01:49:24.654
What are you thinking about?

1467
01:49:25.801 --> 01:49:27.017
Right now

1468
01:49:27.544 --> 01:49:29.636
Watari is coming here Amane

1469
01:49:31.065 --> 01:49:32.693
It was your plan!

1470
01:49:34.049 --> 01:49:34.919
Why Misa?

1471
01:49:35.811 --> 01:49:40.528
For some reason. the 13 day rule didn't work for Amane

1472
01:49:41.732 --> 01:49:43.902
Amane is the Second Kira

1473
01:49:44.672 --> 01:49:46.960
And she has another Death Note

1474
01:49:47.392 --> 01:49:49.181
This is what I'm thinking about

1475
01:49:50.122 --> 01:49:55.714
Then why she didn't write your name when she was freed?

1476
01:49:56.226 --> 01:50:00.319
Probably. she forgot my name she saw at the college

1477
01:50:00.888 --> 01:50:03.009
while she was restrained

1478
01:50:04.759 --> 01:50:06.954
Forgetting things is a girl's nature

1479
01:50:10.507 --> 01:50:11.941
I am going to

1480
01:50:11.976 --> 01:50:14.193
show my face to Amane

1481
01:50:16.657 --> 01:50:17.733
What?

1482
01:50:18.450 --> 01:50:19.847
If you do that. she'll...

1483
01:50:20.348 --> 01:50:22.193
Yes. she'll definitely write my name..

1484
01:50:22.228 --> 01:50:24.768
We can catch her when she's done it

1485
01:50:25.286 --> 01:50:28.717
Let's get her Note

1486
01:50:29.751 --> 01:50:31.793
We never know when and when she'll write

1487
01:50:32.197 --> 01:50:35.718
There are millions of cameras in this building

1488
01:50:35.757 --> 01:50:37.808
What if she didn't bring the Note?

1489
01:50:37.843 --> 01:50:39.618
She'll definitely bring it. This is a huge chance

1490
01:50:40.422 --> 01:50:41.792
to kill me

1491
01:50:45.767 --> 01:50:46.583
All right!

1492
01:50:47.411 --> 01:50:49.567
Then we'll catch her. and restrain her again

1493
01:50:49.602 --> 01:50:51.409
until she tells us about the First Kira

1494
01:50:51.912 --> 01:50:52.974
Is that alright?

1495
01:50:53.742 --> 01:50:55.848
We can definitely make her confess

1496
01:50:56.382 --> 01:50:57.382
as we have the evidence

1497
01:50:58.187 --> 01:51:00.996
You shut out the crew to do this. didn't you?

1498
01:51:01.750 --> 01:51:03.627
If she'll be tied like that again

1499
01:51:04.316 --> 01:51:06.421
She may die this time

1500
01:51:07.576 --> 01:51:09.544
I know I feel sorry. but it can't be helped

1501
01:51:19.998 --> 01:51:21.707
What's the matter Death God?

1502
01:51:34.443 --> 01:51:36.697
Ryuzaki asked me to come

1503
01:51:37.455 --> 01:51:40.681
does it mean he doesn't suspect me as Kira anymore?

1504
01:51:41.328 --> 01:51:42.406
Of course. he doesn't

1505
01:51:56.771 --> 01:51:57.720
But if...

1506
01:51:58.794 --> 01:52:01.108
I couldn't save your life...

1507
01:52:01.743 --> 01:52:04.175
If my heart stops

1508
01:52:04.746 --> 01:52:06.860
this sensor will automatically alert Mr. Yagami

1509
01:52:07.749 --> 01:52:10.296
I've asked him to burn the Death Note

1510
01:52:10.717 --> 01:52:13.009
to never be used again

1511
01:52:18.210 --> 01:52:20.801
Misa's lifespan has been shortened again

1512
01:52:23.012 --> 01:52:23.852
Lifespan?

1513
01:52:24.568 --> 01:52:25.196
What do you mean?

1514
01:52:25.652 --> 01:52:26.225
Ryuzaki

1515
01:52:27.769 --> 01:52:30.084
If you risk your life I'm prepared too

1516
01:52:31.248 --> 01:52:32.758
Let's catch Amane Misa

1517
01:52:32.793 --> 01:52:35.319
...the Second Kira in the act!

1518
01:52:41.457 --> 01:52:42.129
Here she comes

1519
01:53:04.773 --> 01:53:06.727
Yagami Light....

1520
01:53:07.455 --> 01:53:10.108
You've known that this would happen

1521
01:53:11.164 --> 01:53:15.474
Since when I told you that if a Death God expands lifespan of a human

1522
01:53:16.037 --> 01:53:16.868
the Death God will die

1523
01:53:20.225 --> 01:53:22.239
You drove her intoa a corner

1524
01:53:22.274 --> 01:53:23.890
to make me save her

1525
01:53:24.694 --> 01:53:26.845
It will expand her lifespan

1526
01:53:27.529 --> 01:53:28.529
and I will die instead

1527
01:53:30.043 --> 01:53:33.594
That's been your plan from that day

1528
01:53:34.750 --> 01:53:37.210
You'll succeed in killing a Death God!

1529
01:53:38.129 --> 01:53:40.698
You are the true devil

1530
01:53:42.582 --> 01:53:45.627
But still. Misa loves you

1531
01:53:47.553 --> 01:53:48.733
Yagami Light!

1532
01:53:49.547 --> 01:53:52.617
I'll never let you use my Note!

1533
01:53:54.038 --> 01:53:54.810
Misa...

1534
01:53:56.068 --> 01:53:57.428
Even if a short while...

1535
01:53:57.463 --> 01:53:58.796
be happy...

1536
01:54:15.287 --> 01:54:16.131
Watari...!

1537
01:54:16.737 --> 01:54:17.733
Checkmate..!

1538
01:54:42.720 --> 01:54:43.721
Did you use...

1539
01:54:43.756 --> 01:54:44.693
that Death God...?

1540
01:54:47.416 --> 01:54:49.832
Rem has a gentle heart

1541
01:54:52.026 --> 01:54:53.328
Yagami Light...

1542
01:54:56.751 --> 01:54:57.478
I knew it...

1543
01:54:57.675 --> 01:54:58.879
You are the Kira

1544
01:54:59.094 --> 01:55:00.826
I wanted to know your name

1545
01:55:03.345 --> 01:55:04.102
Loser

1546
01:55:06.345 --> 01:55:07.695
I am

1547
01:55:09.729 --> 01:55:10.947
not a...

1548
01:55:19.843 --> 01:55:21.811
Goodbye. L

1549
01:55:23.434 --> 01:55:26.333
You were the best rival

1550
01:55:26.819 --> 01:55:28.286
of me. Kira. the God of the new world.

1551
01:55:29.705 --> 01:55:31.136
If I made a single mistake

1552
01:55:31.989 --> 01:55:33.979
I might've been dead too

1553
01:55:35.655 --> 01:55:37.883
It was a high risk to release Misa

1554
01:55:39.125 --> 01:55:43.921
and let her use Death Note instead of me

1555
01:55:46.760 --> 01:55:49.826
Keep watching me achieving the revolution

1556
01:55:51.463 --> 01:55:54.262
Farewell. L.

1557
01:55:56.777 --> 01:55:57.498
I see...

1558
01:55:57.499 --> 01:56:02.692
She burnt the Note with her

1559
01:56:07.598 --> 01:56:08.556
Light!

1560
01:56:08.591 --> 01:56:09.435
You made it!

1561
01:56:09.470 --> 01:56:10.320
Misa. where's the Note?

1562
01:56:16.661 --> 01:56:18.830
So. you killed L!

1563
01:56:18.831 --> 01:56:20.705
Ryuk! How have you been?

1564
01:56:21.287 --> 01:56:22.890
I won. L is dead

1565
01:56:23.473 --> 01:56:24.718
But I still have a job

1566
01:56:30.520 --> 01:56:32.822
"Yagami Soichiro"

1567
01:56:36.374 --> 01:56:37.795
"Heart attack"

1568
01:56:39.210 --> 01:56:40.897
That's your own father's name. Light!

1569
01:56:41.615 --> 01:56:43.043
To create the new world

1570
01:56:44.620 --> 01:56:45.431
But

1571
01:56:48.746 --> 01:56:50.110
He's your father!

1572
01:56:50.956 --> 01:56:51.864
Why!

1573
01:56:51.865 --> 01:56:53.758
Just shut up!

1574
01:56:54.876 --> 01:56:56.331
No matter how you love something.

1575
01:56:57.299 --> 01:56:58.897
there's the time you have make sacrifices

1576
01:57:00.988 --> 01:57:02.632
I cannot be what I used to be

1577
01:57:08.122 --> 01:57:13.332
"Comes back with the Death Note. gives it to Light and dies"

1578
01:57:45.031 --> 01:57:45.746
Dad...

1579
01:57:55.519 --> 01:57:57.324
Give the Death Note back to me

1580
01:58:01.383 --> 01:58:02.112
Dad

1581
01:58:04.432 --> 01:58:06.483
Since we were young

1582
01:58:07.172 --> 01:58:08.738
You don't forgive even the most insignificant injustice

1583
01:58:09.850 --> 01:58:11.344
and try to be our model father

1584
01:58:12.753 --> 01:58:14.766
I respect you so much

1585
01:58:16.507 --> 01:58:18.329
So I'm sure you'll understand

1586
01:58:19.750 --> 01:58:21.277
What I'm going to do

1587
01:58:23.350 --> 01:58:24.414
What I will achieve

1588
01:58:28.712 --> 01:58:29.321
Dad...

1589
01:58:32.716 --> 01:58:35.735
I'm sorry

1590
01:58:36.660 --> 01:58:37.649
It's your time

1591
01:58:50.225 --> 01:58:51.359
Where's the Death Note?

1592
01:58:51.641 --> 01:58:52.170
Light

1593
01:58:54.316 --> 01:58:55.568
I saw everything

1594
01:59:00.087 --> 01:59:01.390
I watched you through the cameras

1595
01:59:03.267 --> 01:59:04.450
and I heard your voice

1596
01:59:05.448 --> 01:59:06.205
What?

1597
01:59:16.593 --> 01:59:17.576
Light!

1598
01:59:19.185 --> 01:59:20.253
Light!

1599
01:59:21.916 --> 01:59:22.808
You're...

1600
01:59:24.026 --> 01:59:24.874
under arrest

1601
01:59:28.705 --> 01:59:30.306
Light.

1602
01:59:32.294 --> 01:59:33.324
I'm so sad

1603
01:59:34.211 --> 01:59:34.953
we couldn't be friends

1604
01:59:38.715 --> 01:59:39.870
Ryuzaki...?

1605
01:59:42.756 --> 01:59:43.712
You...

1606
01:59:45.406 --> 01:59:46.154
Why...

1607
01:59:53.012 --> 01:59:54.374
A fake notebook!

1608
01:59:56.261 --> 01:59:57.288
Misa. you betrayed me!

1609
01:59:59.031 --> 02:00:00.011
No. I didn't

1610
02:00:01.726 --> 02:00:03.677
How can I betray you?

1611
02:00:04.708 --> 02:00:08.278
No matter how evil you are

1612
02:00:09.805 --> 02:00:11.106
I love you!

1613
02:00:14.352 --> 02:00:16.790
She didn't betray you

1614
02:00:18.530 --> 02:00:21.439
It was unexpected that the Death God acted that way

1615
02:00:24.544 --> 02:00:26.014
This is the real one

1616
02:00:26.546 --> 02:00:28.939
Amane Misa digged out

1617
02:00:31.537 --> 02:00:32.490
And this

1618
02:00:33.486 --> 02:00:36.500
is my real name. which you wanted to know

1619
02:00:40.560 --> 02:00:44.005
You can't change what is written in the Death Note

1620
02:00:44.564 --> 02:00:47.857
which means you won't die until the day written first

1621
02:00:48.568 --> 02:00:51.778
I'll die 20 days later

1622
02:00:52.968 --> 02:00:55.023
so you can't kill me now

1623
02:00:56.543 --> 02:00:57.762
when did you switch them?

1624
02:00:58.545 --> 02:01:01.262
The criminals I punished died as planned

1625
02:01:02.549 --> 02:01:04.040
Yes. on the first day

1626
02:01:05.007 --> 02:01:08.633
Then I concluded that you are the Second Kira

1627
02:01:09.556 --> 02:01:12.037
The 13 day rule is also false

1628
02:01:12.559 --> 02:01:15.390
From the second day. Watari switched it into the fake one

1629
02:01:16.112 --> 02:01:18.205
We were watching it

1630
02:01:19.066 --> 02:01:21.348
and told you a false information

1631
02:01:22.279 --> 02:01:25.837
as if the criminals were killed by Kira

1632
02:01:26.380 --> 02:01:28.537
The biggest goal was. Light

1633
02:01:28.813 --> 02:01:31.965
to confirm that you're Kira

1634
02:01:32.795 --> 02:01:34.328
You're a smart boy

1635
02:01:34.919 --> 02:01:36.468
You didn't give me any clue

1636
02:01:37.026 --> 02:01:38.050
So I decided

1637
02:01:40.039 --> 02:01:41.997
to give up my own life

1638
02:01:42.803 --> 02:01:46.257
This plan couldn't succeed without Mr. Yagami's cooperation

1639
02:01:47.492 --> 02:01:50.190
He is a very sincere person. At first he refused to do it

1640
02:01:51.002 --> 02:01:53.328
But when I showed him my name written in the Note

1641
02:01:53.783 --> 02:01:56.102
I think he understood that I was serious

1642
02:01:56.879 --> 02:01:58.509
Then he finally said yes

1643
02:01:59.440 --> 02:02:01.332
to cooperate with my plan

1644
02:02:03.500 --> 02:02:04.083
He said

1645
02:02:05.483 --> 02:02:06.483
you're not Kira

1646
02:02:07.727 --> 02:02:09.626
he would believe so

1647
02:02:10.069 --> 02:02:11.371
until the last moment

1648
02:02:12.812 --> 02:02:14.707
The cars didn't go to the heliport

1649
02:02:14.742 --> 02:02:16.990
and everyone was watching

1650
02:02:17.621 --> 02:02:19.407
what was happening here

1651
02:02:33.963 --> 02:02:35.002
The saddest thing is

1652
02:02:35.996 --> 02:02:37.639
Watari's death

1653
02:02:38.516 --> 02:02:41.698
I couldn't predict that the Death God would write his name

1654
02:02:43.339 --> 02:02:45.225
That was my last mistake

1655
02:02:46.177 --> 02:02:47.103
Light

1656
02:02:47.773 --> 02:02:49.284
I will understand

1657
02:02:50.262 --> 02:02:52.241
what you are going to do

1658
02:02:52.594 --> 02:02:53.539
you said so

1659
02:02:55.117 --> 02:02:55.725
I'm sorry

1660
02:02:56.555 --> 02:02:57.922
I cannot understand at all

1661
02:02:57.923 --> 02:02:59.603
This isn't justice at all

1662
02:03:04.387 --> 02:03:06.243
Before I got the Death Note

1663
02:03:08.158 --> 02:03:11.546
the world was dead. with tons of criminals that current laws can't punish!

1664
02:03:13.893 --> 02:03:15.275
It was so unreasonable!

1665
02:03:17.142 --> 02:03:18.113
You know what happened

1666
02:03:18.951 --> 02:03:22.059
After Kira appeared. the crime rate decreased 70%

1667
02:03:23.573 --> 02:03:25.697
Isn't that what you want?

1668
02:03:27.142 --> 02:03:28.948
to live in such a peaceful world?

1669
02:03:41.903 --> 02:03:43.545
Light!

1670
02:03:48.910 --> 02:03:51.088
A sheet of the Death Note

1671
