I knew you have it

1672
02:03:53.784 --> 02:03:55.221
You killed Takada with that

1673
02:03:57.139 --> 02:03:58.411
At last.

1674
02:03:59.097 --> 02:04:00.039
I found the last piece

1675
02:04:23.135 --> 02:04:25.135
You're right. I'm the Kira

1676
02:04:26.717 --> 02:04:28.763
I'm God of the new world

1677
02:04:29.864 --> 02:04:30.948
No. you're not

1678
02:04:31.677 --> 02:04:33.496
You are just a murderer

1679
02:04:34.733 --> 02:04:36.131
And this notebook is

1680
02:04:37.079 --> 02:04:39.324
The most horrible lethal weapon ever

1681
02:04:40.417 --> 02:04:41.104
L...

1682
02:04:42.733 --> 02:04:45.600
You don't know. since you don't go out of your cozy room

1683
02:04:46.822 --> 02:04:50.778
You don't know that good people are suffering because of evil people in the world!

1684
02:04:51.487 --> 02:04:53.387
There are tons of evil human beings

1685
02:04:53.921 --> 02:04:55.978
who should disappear for the rest of the people!

1686
02:04:56.336 --> 02:04:59.262
It's impossible to save them with the power of the laws

1687
02:05:01.347 --> 02:05:02.527
Yes. it's impossible

1688
02:05:03.046 --> 02:05:04.130
Laws aren't perfect

1689
02:05:05.574 --> 02:05:07.643
because humans. who created laws that aren't perfect

1690
02:05:08.337 --> 02:05:09.414
It's impossible to be perfect

1691
02:05:11.377 --> 02:05:12.478
However.

1692
02:05:12.513 --> 02:05:16.427
the lawas are evidence of human's struggle to be righteous

1693
02:05:18.703 --> 02:05:20.044
You are egotistical

1694
02:05:21.483 --> 02:05:25.471
It must never be allowed to rob someone's life based on ego!

1695
02:05:30.057 --> 02:05:32.134
It's wasteful to talk with you!

1696
02:05:35.300 --> 02:05:36.091
Ryuk!

1697
02:05:38.651 --> 02:05:40.519
Ryuk. where are you

1698
02:05:42.318 --> 02:05:43.454
Hi there

1699
02:05:45.949 --> 02:05:47.273
Oh. another Death God

1700
02:05:48.694 --> 02:05:50.629
Can everyone see it. as you all have touched the Note?

1701
02:05:55.397 --> 02:05:56.187
Ryuk...

1702
02:05:59.319 --> 02:06:01.325
I'll show you something fun

1703
02:06:03.359 --> 02:06:04.714
Kill them all

1704
02:06:06.741 --> 02:06:08.474
Kill them all right now!

1705
02:06:11.183 --> 02:06:12.061
Light!

1706
02:06:12.921 --> 02:06:16.880
What are you waiting for?
Write their names. hurry

1707
02:06:19.510 --> 02:06:21.478
All right. I'll write it down

1708
02:06:22.931 --> 02:06:23.932
Don't!

1709
02:06:23.967 --> 02:06:25.475
Stop!

1710
02:06:43.595 --> 02:06:44.815
It's no use...

1711
02:06:46.644 --> 02:06:47.571
Ryuk...

1712
02:06:47.606 --> 02:06:49.342
Are you done yet?

1713
02:06:49.747 --> 02:06:50.769
yep

1714
02:06:52.881 --> 02:06:53.671
Show me

1715
02:06:54.929 --> 02:06:56.568
See

1716
02:06:58.777 --> 02:06:59.777
"Yagami Light"

1717
02:07:07.908 --> 02:07:09.026
Too bad!

1718
02:07:09.687 --> 02:07:11.333
You've been too much

1719
02:07:11.916 --> 02:07:13.434
dependent on me

1720
02:07:14.176 --> 02:07:15.198
Wait...

1721
02:07:15.505 --> 02:07:17.761
I said...
I'd show you something fun!

1722
02:07:20.922 --> 02:07:23.823
You've shown me enough

1723
02:07:24.914 --> 02:07:26.039
You've enjoyed enough too

1724
02:07:26.928 --> 02:07:28.441
What are you talking about!

1725
02:07:28.930 --> 02:07:30.541
Nothing has started yet!

1726
02:07:31.403 --> 02:07:33.027
Oh. I almost forgot to say

1727
02:07:33.982 --> 02:07:35.678
A human who used the Death Note

1728
02:07:36.300 --> 02:07:39.337
cannot goto heaven nor hell

1729
02:07:40.272 --> 02:07:42.376
After you die. you'll see

1730
02:07:44.743 --> 02:07:45.743
nought!

1731
02:07:55.924 --> 02:07:57.614
Light!

1732
02:07:58.927 --> 02:08:00.842
Why. Ryuk. why?

1733
02:08:01.525 --> 02:08:03.209
I can't die here!

1734
02:08:03.722 --> 02:08:05.340
Light!

1735
02:08:08.198 --> 02:08:09.267
Why?

1736
02:08:10.330 --> 02:08:13.447
I was always trying to do the right thing

1737
02:08:14.286 --> 02:08:17.227
You tought me what justice is. Dad

1738
02:08:17.262 --> 02:08:20.872
Why do I have to die like this!

1739
02:08:35.323 --> 02:08:37.562
Kira is. the justice...

1740
02:08:40.311 --> 02:08:41.082
Dad..

1741
02:08:42.951 --> 02:08:45.339
Please understand me...

1742
02:08:50.998 --> 02:08:51.763
Light?

1743
02:09:02.862 --> 02:09:03.926
You idiot..

1744
02:09:38.752 --> 02:09:40.730
I will clean out

1745
02:09:41.635 --> 02:09:43.603
every Death Note

1746
02:09:44.374 --> 02:09:46.225
You don't want to use it?

1747
02:09:47.501 --> 02:09:49.834
Oh. I'm soooo bored!

1748
02:10:20.109 --> 02:10:21.594
I reported the eveen to the superiors

1749
02:10:23.291 --> 02:10:25.610
I couldn't say anything about the Death Note though

1750
02:10:26.063 --> 02:10:28.282
I reported everything to ICPO

1751
02:10:28.982 --> 02:10:30.955
They couldn't understand

1752
02:10:32.063 --> 02:10:35.065
Kira's death won't be announced

1753
02:10:37.471 --> 02:10:39.677
Light was killed by Kira...

1754
02:10:40.164 --> 02:10:42.040
It's the truth

1755
02:10:42.557 --> 02:10:45.463
I told Sachiko and Sayu

1756
02:10:47.359 --> 02:10:49.748
Amane has lost her memory about the Death Note again

1757
02:10:51.151 --> 02:10:54.100
Because we burned both notebooks

1758
02:10:55.326 --> 02:10:56.598
Ryuzaki

1759
02:10:58.934 --> 02:11:00.845
I can't say a word for you

1760
02:11:02.269 --> 02:11:03.138
I'm sorry

1761
02:11:04.677 --> 02:11:05.677
It's me

1762
02:11:07.119 --> 02:11:08.955
who has to apologize

1763
02:11:10.254 --> 02:11:12.140
I couldn't even save Light

1764
02:11:13.689 --> 02:11:14.334
Ryuzaki.

1765
02:11:15.825 --> 02:11:17.503
I'm happy to fight along with you

1766
02:11:18.141 --> 02:11:19.196
I"m proud of you

1767
02:11:21.422 --> 02:11:24.347
It's my time. let me be alone

1768
02:11:27.177 --> 02:11:28.348
I don't know

1769
02:11:30.313 --> 02:11:32.063
What kind of people my parents are

1770
02:11:33.771 --> 02:11:34.912
But I know. Mr. Yagami

1771
02:11:35.633 --> 02:11:37.279
You are a great father

1772
02:11:37.502 --> 02:11:38.277
also to me

1773
02:11:40.290 --> 02:11:41.455
Ryuzaki...

1774
02:11:45.017 --> 02:11:46.764
Goodbye. Mr. Yagami

1775
02:11:48.288 --> 02:11:49.492
And thank you

1776
02:12:30.419 --> 02:12:32.387
One year later

1777
02:12:44.159 --> 02:12:47.020
It's the first time we baked a birthday cake for Light

1778
02:12:47.509 --> 02:12:49.155
after he graduated kindergarten

1779
02:12:51.093 --> 02:12:53.892
After he entered elementary school. I started buying it every year

1780
02:12:54.409 --> 02:12:56.358
I remembe that I blew out the candles

1781
02:12:56.411 --> 02:12:57.995
I asked him right?

1782
02:12:58.539 --> 02:13:01.329
Your brother let you do it

1783
02:13:02.286 --> 02:13:03.796
even though it was his birthday

1784
02:13:04.395 --> 02:13:06.142
He was so kind to you

1785
02:13:11.393 --> 02:13:13.314
Mom. look!
It's snowing

1786
02:13:15.006 --> 02:13:16.007
Sayu. bring an umbrella to the station for Dad

1787
02:13:36.250 --> 02:13:37.299
Dad!

1788
02:13:37.889 --> 02:13:39.594
Oh. thanks

1789
02:13:44.241 --> 02:13:45.814
Shall we share it?

1790
02:13:48.651 --> 02:13:52.287
After Kira disappeared. is the crime rate increasing?

1791
02:13:53.402 --> 02:13:56.090
Do you think the world still needs Kira?

1792
02:13:56.405 --> 02:13:57.679
No. I don't

1793
02:13:58.076 --> 02:13:59.431
Kira... killed my...

1794
02:14:07.416 --> 02:14:11.049
Light fought against Kira. until the very last moment

1795
02:14:12.062 --> 02:14:13.269
I know...

1796
02:14:14.478 --> 02:14:15.852
I know. Dad

1797
02:14:28.108 --> 02:14:29.831
Happy birthday

1798
02:14:32.407 --> 02:14:34.526
I feel like I...

1799
02:14:35.326 --> 02:14:37.346
forgot something very important

1800
02:14:40.214 --> 02:14:40.996
But...

1801
02:14:42.807 --> 02:14:45.416
I can't remember anything!

1802
02:14:53.395 --> 02:14:55.176
Light....

